author: @violet-tq5ul
text:
I cried while listening to this song without understanding much but it made me so emotional multiple times. And just recently, I looked up the lyrics translated into English, I found myself just weeping and sobbing. 

Thank you Woozi, Bumzu and all the members for putting out such beautiful pieces of art in the world. I became a carat around 2 years ago, but each season I get stuck on new songs that were released years ago. Before becoming a carat, K-pop songs rarely could make me cry, but with Seventeen..there are separate playlists for such moments. It's so beautiful that we all as human beings can feel such deep and intense emotions when listening to creations of other just the same human beings. There's so much love and admiration that I can't seem to put into words. I just hope that all the members feel loved and fulfilled. 

while there's seventeen, there's hope in life.

author: @unshallowkyeomie
text:
Nah I'm always late to masterpieces ğŸ˜­
I recently discovered this song, and from Carat's comments and the emotions they brought on this song (that's why I fell in love with Seventeen, they're such a storyteller, full of emotions) I've known the meaning without even need to search the full translation. Beautiful
Another thing I love about them, we don't really need any other guitar cover or remixes from anyone because they already did it themselves. 
The first time I heard this song, I really love Woozi's intro with the guitar... But the continuation of the song is really not what I expected, 'cause I really want the guitar to somehow still going throughout the song or at least popped again at some part of the song. But no.. 
So here I am today, searching a guitar cover of this song, and delighted to find this, another acoustic ver. by Seventeen themselves and I absolutely LOVE this version more. It needs to be on music streaming services ğŸ˜ğŸ‰
Now I feel guilty for being reallllyy late to join this fandom ğŸ¥²ğŸ¥²ğŸ©·ğŸ©µ

Baru ngeh sama liriknya. Nangis bangett.

"Sayang, tidak apa apa." 
"Cintaku hanya sebesar ini. Namun hatiku tidak akan berubah."
"Aku akan menjadi musim semimu di semua musim dingin." 
"Kamu selalu berada di sisiku." 
"Terimakasih sayangku." 
"Aku benar benar minta maaf." 
"Aku bisa melakukan apapun untukmu." 
"Aku tidak bisa melakukan apapun." 

Nae sarang.

text: Can we talk abt how realistic artists are svt. Like this song basically says that they are sorry for loving us only as their fans, "my love only amounts to this" and how they want to give so much to us than just a song and its lyrics... but also sends the mssg that they are so thankful for us to love them nonetheless, "it's alright, it's okay, I'm more thankful of you".i have never heard a more realistic song. Most songs that idols dedicate to their fans basically say that wanna stay with them forever and how they will do anything for them but we know those are really unrealistic things to say, but here we have svt giving us a song that defines our relationship with them which them being so thankful to us for our presence and words of encouragement that it's their biggest strength

And all they want is to be a comforting presence in our lives. That making a positive impact, is what they strive for. And it makes me feel comforted that as much as I helped them, they helped me in return by doing their best and showing me amazing music. There's nothing I appreciate more. Dear Carats,

*Happy 6th Anniversary! It hasn't been long since I've been a Carat, but it was my BEST decision knowing SEVENTEEN! I may not know you guys, but thanks for being a Carat with me! I appreciate ALL the hard work SEVENTEEN did! I still CAN'T believe it's already been 6 years. I'll be a Carat forever from now on, I will always remember SEVENTEEN EVEN when they disband! Tears in my eyes... I've lost count of how many times I've watched this now... 

Today, from the moment Jihoon began to sing, my eyes caught on the sunlight glowing against his hair.
The twinkling chimes before the bass comes in...
The clarity of Chan's voice, the confidence in Mingyu's. 
How Seungcheol pours out a feeling I'll never understand into his microphone. 

There are just... layers to this experience. Every time.

I couldn't hear the lyrics well because I was focused on SEVENTEEN's face and focused on the scenery, but when I listened to it for the third time, I realized that the lyrics were really sad. This is the only love I have, but when I said thank you for being by my side, I cried without knowing it. Looking at it like this, I think the lyrics are really well written... It's sadder to say baby at the end... When I imagine the situation according to the lyrics, it's sadder than I thought... It's been a while since I've liked Seventeen, but most of the members also sing I was amazed at how much he rapping... It's great to rap and sing, but I thought it was great because he put emotion into such a sad song. I saw a comment on a Seventeen video, and it was a comment that Seventeen's song is like a musical. The title song "Ready to Love" released this time is also like a musical, so it's no secret to play it every morning and prepare to go out ğŸ˜… I think I want to live as Seventeen for the rest of my life. Seventeen is so overflowing with their own charms that it is impossible to decide on such a thing as a favorite Cha-ae. I didn't have a long life, but I think he's probably the best idol in my life. Even when I grow old, I want to remember Seventeen.

author: @KennieKemala
text:
Hello seventeen and carat,

I know it's already passed May 26 and i guess it's never too late to pour my feelings toward our 6 year journey

It was not short, honestly it was long journey. I almost have seen all the ups and downs we've been through. Being each other strength for 6 years it was never been easy and it's overwhelming that our feeling towards each other still firmly stay the same, like i can't believe it you trust me as much as i do, you love me as much as i do.

Words never been enough to say everything that i feel towards you guys really..i just conclude all these feelings for you guys with my sincere gratitude, i hope you understand that i can't give you any materialistic things but i hope my gratitude could touch your heart so you guys could atleast feel ease and warm.

Once again, happy birthday :)

author: @huangrenjunism
text:
forgive me for this cheesy and mildly cringe long essay comment in advance lol. but svt deserves it <3

so i was gonna write a really long comment of how much i'm proud of seventeen, how much i love and adore them, how much i want to support them, and how their journey to come where they are will never cease to impress me and make me emotional. but i can't even put it into words, which may sound a bit cheesy lol, so i'm just gonna wing it.
seventeen has always felt like a place to call home, even though they are just thirteen people across the world on the internet. but somehow they have succeeded into bringing so many different and beautiful types of people together and giving them a makeshift home. even when i don't watch svt content/music for awhile, i can always come back to them and immediately feel endless amounts of warmth and love that brings such a large amount of happiness. they love us so much and we love them back, but they have also taught us to not rely on them. they have taught us to love others and ourselves and to not make them the center of lives. they make me, and i'm sure many other people, appreciate the people and things around me, and i genuinely adore them for that. i don't think i could ever express how amazed i am by the endless amounts of love and talent they have. i guess you could say their power of love is truly astonishing *wink wink* (sorry to anyone who read that lmfao)
happy (3 days late) 6th anniversary loves, you deserve all the success and love in the world. thank you so much for everything <3

author: @blackplasticbagandgraytowe9169
text:
Seventeen,, 13 angels,, stanning them is the best decision in my life.

I have been stanning them since 2018, after they release 'Thanks' song. I really can't describe how precious that song bringing me into diamond life. 

After listening to that song ,, I start listen to their song since debut to learn all things about them.

Yeah, they songs really... I can't describe how much beautiful their song are.. Not just one, two or three of their songs,, I'm telling you the truth, *all of their songs* .

Since that time,, my life become happier than before. I really can't tell you how much I feel grateful to have them in my life. 

That year,, 2018,, I feel that year really worst year for me. Being compared to other student, being push to study hard for exam, I really feel down when I'm not doing my best in exam because I'm scared to make mistake. Really,, I really hate myself that time. 

But,, since I start stanning them,, I found my inspiration to be my own self and don't care to what other people are saying to me. Even my parents always comparing me to my classmate.

But, I'm glad, Seventeen was coming into my life.

They are everything for me since that time.

Trust me, you won't regret stanning them.

Choi Seungcheol
Yoon Jeonghan
Hong Jisoo
Wen Junhui
Kwon Soonyoung
Jeon Wonwoo
Lee Jihoon
Lee Seokmin
Kim Mingyu
Xu Minghao
Boo Seungkwan
Chwe Hansol
Lee Chan 

Thank you , SEVENTEENğŸ’ğŸ’™

author: @hoshtete
text: I just joined the fandom this year. Since last December, I have been listening to your songs on repeat. I got addicted to you so bad and so damn fast. Your songs provide me so much strength and a sense of safety. Every video I have watched of you guys has given me so much laughter, so much joy, inspiration and soooooo much love. I have never fallen for any artist this fast before. It really is overwhelming. But you make me genuinely happy. I will never regret loving seventeen. I promise that I will be here for a very very long time to come. Till the last say the name, and even after that, all 13 members will forever have their own little place in my heart. Thank you so much, for just being you. Next year, for the 7th anniversary, I will be even for grateful for all the love you have given me, for all the times you made me laugh, for all the times you were there with me when i was crying, for every lesson I learnt from you. Thank you, thank you.

author: @deepmoon3189
text:
For Seventeen. I don't know maybe you woudln't see this comment but hear me please. 
It was November 2019, i found you and i was just ignoring Don't Wanna Cry and just love it as a song. It was my hard time as a teenager, I was about to giving up. I don't care anything about my life anymore.
But then your songs keep show up in my youtube, like it was a fate. I don't know why i clicked all of those vids, you guys slowly encourage me up, i also gradually get my smile back. 
I don't know what would happen to me if I didn't find seventeen that day. until now, December 24th 2019 has been a special day for me, you saved me Seventeen. ğŸ’â¤ï¸

author: @jenrawlings1
text:
What an amazing group of people! Isn't it inspiring how 13 people can come together from within Korea, China and the USA to form a group like this. It really just goes to show no matter where you're from, what your mother language is, if you're an introvert or extrovert, if you believe within yourself and never give up on your dreams you can make it. 
Happy 6 years Seventeen!                                  To all Carats, no matter where we are from, what gender we identify as, if we are introverted or extroverted, our past and our struggles, we are here today.  We may not all know each other personally but every single one of us together makes our fandom what it is. I am so proud to say that i am a Carat and to be apart of this beautiful fandom. Thank you Carats and most importantly thank you Seventeen. With you till the end! <3

author: @dindaseptiara5393
text:
congratulations, we succeeded to reach 6 years together. looking back to old days, it feels like miracle how a "nugu" could top the big three. for a group that coming from almost bankrupt agency, that certainly wasn't a smooth journey at all--you guys poured tears and bloods into it, I know that.

I remember Seungcheol said that he lost his counts and always wonder when will the debut happen. I remember how Jeonghan stuttered when MC-ing a music show. I remember Jisoo used to be an underdog member and people barely recognize him. I remember Junhui and his confident ass left his hometown just to be a singer and gets only 2 lines in a song. I remember Soonyoung smiled towards the screen when you guys having a debut showcase and only some people stopped to watch you perform. I remember Wonwoo and his underground rapper hairstyle that I used to mock because you'd do as well if only you saw his pics. I remember the way Jihoon couldn't stop crying when you guys won the music champ for the first time. I remember Seokmin snotted his nose out because the judge said he wasn't really qualified for a main vocalist. I remember Mingyu came to the audition wearing a pair of slipper. I remember Minghao used to cry himself to sleep because he was a new kid and barely understand Korean. I remember Seungkwan promoted Jeju better than SK government ever did--he still does, though. I remember Hansol was shorter than Jisoo and also his gold quote. I remember Chan who's maknae but feels more like hyung than the rest of them. thirteen of you grew like big, nice sunflower. that damn green cubicle basement wasn't there to witness nothing.

thank you for all these years, you guys always accompany me in my ups and downs. your music made me realize that we can always see the beauty through the worst things, some of your lyrics made me grow as a human. thanks to those imaginary support when I feel like no one would understand.

happy 6th anniversary, let's stay together for longerğŸ’™

author: @drjeonwonwoo4996
text:
This 6 years feels so fast. At first, i got to know them bcus my bias was Cheollie when he's still Pledis Boys with Nuest. Knowing he not passing to debut with Nuest breaks my heart but I still follow him and discovers these gems. They were rough at first and now they're the shiniest diamonds. Following them since trainee days and crying when they announced their debut date (ancient carats knew the hard days they went through). Since I am the same age with 95 liners, feels their journey is also mine. They taught me loving myself, loving people around me and to give back what I've gained. Currently, my bias is Wonwoo and my bias list being wrecked so many times with no regrets. Crying when they won their first music show, crying when they announced our name is Carat, crying whenever they did something out of love for Carats. 
Till the last 'Say The Name'

author: @berrypeach1012
text:
Seventeen always feels like home. A wonderful place you can go back whenever you're feeling down. A place where you can share your laughter and tears... A place where you can feel that you can love yourself.

well, this is how I feel... I found them during the time I was very sad and confused back in 2013. It's nice to see how the young boys I was only watching on the green room is now one of the most respected groups in Kpop.
It's been so long, and they still feel like home... listening to their comforting words and songs...
I know seventeen will never know how much they helped me on my journey of loving myself. But I would like to say thank you for everything... It's been so long, and my feelings may not be as intense as when I started back then, but my love, trust, and respect for this men still remain the same.
I sometimes feel like a proud mom even tho I only have the same age as the 97line ã…‹ã…‹
But really... Thank you for always sharing such wonderful songs. Your songs keep me going everyday... Happy 6th Anniversary of your debut!

I hope the best for SEVENTEEN and to all CARATs who are supporting them in a positive way. New and Old fans, we are a family that love the same people.
Let's all continue to be the fans Seventeen can be proud of â™¡

author: @caratyooniverse4533
text:
The fact that they kept on saying that they'll improve so that no one can say anything bad about us and that we can proudly say that we are a carat hits so different. Like the love isnt one-sided at all. They love us as much as we love them but what makes it more beautiful is that there is still this boundary that they have set y'know? Just like what minghao kept on saying that we shouldn't supposed to be making them as a center of our lives and that instead of treating them as a significant other we can treat them as an inspiration. After all he accepts that not all of us will stay until thr very end. And that all of this might just be a phase but they are still thankful bc they were once part of our youth.

During in-complete concert cheol said something like it is their responsibility to overturn what other people could say about us being a fan. Because as we all know some people would really think that we are crazy or would think badly about us for being a fan. Sometimes calling us obsessed, immature. But hearing these kind of words from them and assuring us as if they 'got us' means so freaking special to me as a fanğŸ˜­

You know, that's just so beautiful. The way they value the  people who loves and support them is just out of this world and too good to be true but it actually is!! And I'm so happy to have them as my idols.

author: @sittizaenab4048
text:
Pengen share ini,
Aku tahu mereka dari akhir 2018,
Awalnya iseng cari diyoutube, list lagu2 populer kpop dan yang muncul sebuah channel aku lupa apa dan muncul 1 lagu dari seventeen " thanks "
Denger lagunya itu keren kemudian aku cari lagunya digoogle dan ke dow nload. " thanks " selalu kuputar dan penasaran ini seventeen siapa2 aja dan gimana dancenya. Serius keren dan menyentuh banget padahal itu belum tahu artinya pertama nonton lagu ini di salah satu channel music show kpop. 

Nah penasaran lah saya sama mereka lagi dengan cari2 single mereka, download dan dengerin, smuanya keren.
Terus kuputuskan untuk mengenal lagi mereka dengan nonton idol room,reality show mereka yang dipulau yoesodo dan yg di Jepang. Jadi suka sama mereka. Ini ditahun 2019. Kemudian nonton video2 mereka yg going seventeen versi dulunya mereka sampe sekarang.
Itu berlanjut sampai tahun 2020. Ditahun ini,  aku mulai ngikutin mereka baik-baik dengan follow semua sosmednya seventeen. sampe download vlive hanya untuk lihat mereka. Follow akun fan Indonesia di telegram buat tahu info weverse mereka krn aku ngak bisa punya itu.
Hingga sekarang. Aku udah cinta sama mereka. Aku emang suka kpop tapi bukan tipe nge stan bucin gitu2, ngak.cm skdar suka. Dari semuanya, cuma SEVENTEEN yang buat hatiku nyaman dan memutuskan buat sayang, cinta dan respect sm mereka sampai sekarang.
Mereka adalah mood booster bangetttt... 
 
Lagu ini betul2 ngungkapin perasaan mereka ke carat. Dan aku ngerasain pesan mereka. Bersyukur banget. 
T

Terima kasih kalian,
Semoga kalian sehat2, tetap semangat, menjadi pribadi yg lebih baik untuk diri kaliam sendiri, keluarga, teman2, dan fans kalian, carat.
Kami, carat, selalu mendukung kalian, 
Kami bangga punya kalian, SEVENTEEN

#maaf panjang, curahan hati banget ini hehehe

author: @amethystcorsage8409
text:
Hello, this is my Love Letter for you. 

Here I want to tell you the story when I'm Falling for You guys. When the very first time you guys Come To Me, my life was so dark. I'm at the worst time (until now btw). I have to deal it with my Trauma. Fear is the one I should deal with every day. But since I know you guys for the past 7 months, whenever I'm tired I always Run to You. U guys such a Healing for me. Besides my 'dark' life whenever I see you I feel like I have a Second Life. 

My first era was Home;Run. I was clueless back then since you're 13 members and I was tired to remember all of you. So I tried again with your Q&A content on Youtube. I Don't Know why but the more I watch the more I want to know. So, since that day I became a CARAT and watch all your contents. 

From now on, I always Thinking About You for 247 in my life (I swear!). I really Adore U guys so much. The way you write your Hit Song (all of your songs is just a hit song for me), the way you build your relationship with everyone, the positive vibe that you always show us. Keep up Bring It. You're really Good to Me ay ay ay. 

Guys I really wanna say Thanks for being my Home. If I have a chance I really want to Hug all of you, showing how grateful I am for slipping into this diamond life. At this specific time  you're already become the Highlight of my life. I Wish we Can't See The End of our journey bcs we will always Together forever. If only the end is coming hopefully it would be a Happy Ending. 

I'm tearing up right now ã…  but I Don't Wanna Cry
All My Love just for you
I do Crazy in Love with all of you
ì•„ì£¼ Nice to know you 
I'm so lucky for having you
Once again, Let Me Hear You Say
SAY THE NAME!

author: @nurrizkaalfirahusna9647
text:
Sebagai penikmat lagu K-Pop sejak 2015, aku udah biasa denger lagu berbagai girl group atau boy grup. Awal tahu Seventeen dari lagu Mansae mereka, dan sejak itu selalu ngikutin comeback mereka tapi ga bener2 sesuka itu sama mereka. Sebatas menikmati semua lagu dan video dance mereka karena mereka sangat berbakat. Baru tahun kemarin, aku kayak bener2 sayang sama mereka bertiga belas. Rasanya agak menyesal kenapa ga dari dulu, dari awal dengar lagu mereka, aku mulai serius memperhatikan mereka.

Jujur. semua lagu seventeen ga ada yang gagal. Terima kasih atas lagu-lagu indahnya. Lagu-lagu Seventeen ini adalah teman yang menemaniku mengerjakan tugas selama ini. Dan kalau disuruh lagu apa yang membuat aku bisa menitikkan air mata sebelum tahu artinya, lagu ini adalah salah satunya. Apalagi pas tahu artinya, makin ambyar. 

Sekali lagi, Terima kasih banyak Seventeen.

author: @saskiaekklesia5551
text:
Happy 6th anniversary, my boys!

I might not always be there for you... But you guys... Your music, its always there to cheer me up when I'm sad, always comfort me when I need to be comforted, always filling me up when I feel empty, and of course you guys are always there when I'm happy. I would like to thank you guys for that.

This past 6 years must not be that easy, right?
But thank you, for not giving up on music.
Thank you, for standing tall through all the hard times you must've been.
Thank you, for not giving up to see us, CARATS. Especially to see us happy.
Thank you, for all of your hard work. You always nailed it, guys.
Thank you, for being the most amazing group that we all known: SEVENTEEN!

On this beautiful 6th anniversary, let's mark it with all of our love, joy, and happines!!
I will always look up to you, boys.
Always.

See you on your 7th, 8th, 9th, 10th, and infinity anniversary because we know... Even if our youth is over, even if we have to go on our own journey, but we will always have each other. 
We will always belong to each other. 
So don't worry, no one will get left behind and feel lonely, because we are always one <333

I love you guys so so so so so much.
THANK YOU SEVENTEEN!

author: @aliasfrmdn
text:
aku gatau harus pake kata apalagi buat ngegambarin rasa terima kasihku ke kalian secara singkat, padat, dan jelas. orang orang mungkin ngeliatnya kalian hanya boygroup kpop. tp buatku, kalian lebih dari itu.

..penyelamat? ya, penyelamat mungkin adalah kata yang paling bisa menjelaskan secara singkat, meskipun aku masih belum puas sama kata itu.

aku pernah ngerasa hilang. kaya ngga ada tujuan hidup. ngga tau apa yang mau aku lakuin besok, minggu depan, bulan depan, tahun depan, lima, delapan, atau bahkan 10 tahun ke depan. bahkan sampe berdoa kalo tuhan akan ambil nyawaku tiap kali aku tidur, dan terbangun dengan rasa kesal karena ngga dikabulin doaku itu. iya, seperti cuma melayang-layang aja di semesta; gaada gunanya, nyampah doang malah.

people asked me to love myself, but i also need something to push me so i can love myself. and im proud to say you're one of the reasons.

semua lagu kalian yang dibuat dengan hati sampai dengan selamat dan apik di hatiku. cara kalian perlakukan carat, meskipun bukan aku secara spesifik, bener-bener buatku yang cuma bisa ngeliat ngerasa.. nyaman. kalian pun enjoy ngejalaninnya meskipun kalo kata orang orang "ini hanyalah pekerjaan mereka".

dan dengan lagu ini, kalian menyampaikan permintaan maaf kalian karena kalian "hanya bisa memberikan cinta sebesar ini". aku gatau untuk carat lain, tapi buatku pribadi ini udah jauh dari kata cukup.

meskipun aku masih belum tau aku mau ngapain di masa depan nanti, seengganya sekarang aku ngga ngerasa kalo aku cuma melayang-layang kaya sampah di alam semesta ini. seengganya doa doaku untuk dicabut nyawanya ngga keluar dari bibir dan hatiku lagi. seengganya aku udah ngga merasa "hilang" sepenuhnya.

karena kalian. iya, kalian bertiga belas. seungcheol, jeonghan, joshua, junhui, soonyoung, wonwoo, jihoon, myeongho, mingyu, seokmin, seungkwan, hansol, chan, dan seventeen yang menyatukan kalian sampe detik ini, dan semoga sampai nanti juga.

aku mungkin cuma satu dari sekian juta banyaknya carat di dunia ini. mungkin kalian juga engga bakal baca ini karena keterbatasan bahasa. tapi makasih, banget. aku bersyukur tuhan ngga mengabulkan doaku waktu itu.

makasih banyak. makasih. makasih. ğŸ¤ğŸ’

author: @ElleCheu
text:
Dear, SEVENTEEN
Terima kasih karena telah membuat kami merasa di rumah. Meski rumahku bukan tempat yang hangat dan diidamkan. Terima kasih telah mengisi hari-hari keputusasaanku dengan kebahagiaan. Terima kasih telah membawaku termotivasi untuk menjadi produktif. Terima kasih telah memanjakan kami. Suara cantik itu, gerakan indah itu, senyuman kebahagiaan kalian, terima kasih untuk semuanya! Aku merasa sedih tidak bisa mengungkapkan perasaanku dengan baik. Aku merasa tidak layak mencintai kalian. Sungguh, aku minta maaf. Aku tidak mampu membalas perasaan kalian dengan baik. Kalian terlalu baik, sangat baik.

author: @maygomez6001
text:
Hi Seventeen,

I am one of those fans  that you've saved from frustration and exhaustion from the quarantine life. Thank you for sharing your music to me. For giving me amazing contents, for making me feel loved and comforting me with your words, letters, and lyrics. You don't know how much that means to me. 

Your loved is overwhelming. I sometimes ask myself if you can also feel our love too. Am I  reciprocating your love enough? Am I taking you for granted? Are my  efforts enough to show you that I care? If I can, i want to give everything you deserves. 

I take pride of being a Carat. Imagine I am a fan of 13 amazing, talented, all rounder and well rounded artists. I feel blessed. You are not just idols for me. You are artists. You are one of my comfort zones (mentally and emotionally). You are a family to me. Don't worry, I manage my time being a fan. Hehe. I still have life outside of the fandom. 

There's a possibility that you might not be a able to read this and that's okay. I just want to say how much grateful I am to all of you. 

All My Love, 
Mich

author: @jihooniejellybean8793
text:
T-T  It's our birthday but I'm grateful for their existence. I known and grown with the since debut,  maybe it's because we are close in age but  they are the only group I feel really connected to. I feel like I matured along with them and maybe that's why their songs always connect with the most.                                                 
They have been with me through happy and hard times, unknowingly making me laugh and  giving me words of encouragement/ comfort through their songs and simply talks. 
I don't know how to explain it but when I'm happy their songs make me happier, when I'm sad their songs feel like a hug  and when I'm suffocated/exhausted their songs feel like fresh air. Although some songs do make me feel like  someone just broke  my heart even though I'm single. 
They are are one of the few things that heal me from this fast paced life we live, that  to me often feels like more work than it's worth since it so fragile. 
I hope us(Carats) and Seventeen can continue to make memories with each other for years to come. I'm grateful to be part of this fandom.
THANK YOU CARATS WHO HAVE MADE THIS POSSIBLE!

author: @gecarat
text:
Happy 6th anniversary Seventeen,
Ga kerasa udah 6 tahun juga bareng-bareng sama kalian..
inget banget dulu masa-masa susah nyelesaiin skripsi berjuang untuk lulus, disitu ku menemukan kalian yang lagi berjuang juga untuk debut..

Ngeliat kalian waktu itu buat aku mutusin dukung kalian terus, kayak aku ga akan biarin kalian ga ternotice orang-orang, semua orang harus tau ada kalian yang sangat-sangat berbakat, kalau ternyata kedepannya sulit aku bakal selalu ada disini ngedukung kalian, ga akan biarin kalian berjuang sendiri.. dan aku masih disini sampai hari ini dan Insya Allah dimasa yang akan datang sampai umur memisahkan..

Jadi kpopers dari 2008 tapi baru kalian yang buat aku tergerak pokoknya aku bakal dukung banget, harus beli album.Ketika aku berniat untuk support kalian saat itu aku bener-bener ngelakuin semua hal yang pertama kali selama aku jadi kpopers.. aku tau kalian sebenernya udah cukup lama, 2012/2013? jadi kpopers 2nd gen buat aku banyak tau grup-grup kpop dan itu yang buat aku kenal sama kakak2 kalian, after school, nuest, hello venus. terus denger kabar kalau akan debutin grup dengan member 17 orang, wow banget rasanya.. awalnya ngeliat kalian sekilas doang dari nontonin 17tv, liatin kalian di mv kakak2 kalian, belum belum tergerak untuk cari tau lebih lanjut saat itu, sampai awal tahun 2015 februari atau maret gitu aku denger kabar kalian bakal debut baru aku kepo dengan nontonin video-video latihan kalian, nontonin 17project,  ngeliat gimana usaha kalian ngeliat kepribadian kalian.. buat aku bener-bener jatuh hati sama kalian. 

Kalian adalah anak-anak yang pertama kali buat aku bela-belain cari tau gimana cara live streaming andromeda, live streaming debut plan kalian, gimana cara aku live streaming semua acara music show di korea yang kalian datengin buat perform, caranya live streaming radio di korea buat dengerin kalian kalau lagi ada schedule, gimana caranya aku voting buat kalian ketika masuk nominasi, semua schedule kalian aku ikutin satu-satu.. walaupin kita jauh aku pastikan aku selalu ada disini untuk support kalian, aku selalu ngedampingin kalian walau kalian ga liat aku, hehe..

Kalian beberapa kali masuk nominasi di music show, ga menang bukan berarti aku berhenti buat berusaha lebih keras untuk promosiin dan voting kalian, 4 Mei 2016 sehari setelah aku ulang tahun, kalian tau? salah satu doaku saat itu adalah semoga kalian bisa menang.. dan hari itu doaku dikabulkan.. Pretty U first Win.. nangis, nangis banget sampai gemeter saking senangnya, aku seneng bisa ngeliat kalian nangis bahagia, aku janji bakal ngasih kalian lebih banyak tangis bahagia kedepannya..

Shining Diamond fanmeeting 2016, aku bersyukur ada kesempatan bisa ketemu kalian langsung.. aku yang belum ada kesempatan ngeliat kalian di korea bisa liat kalian di Jakarta. salah satu kenangan bareng kalian yang ga akan aku lupain, bisa liat kalian sedeket itu sampai high touch sama kalian di akhir acara.. hehe udahannya aku gemeteran banget sampai nangis, makasih Seventeen udah dateng untuk ketemu kita-kita di Jakarta..

Perjuangan kita diawal emang berat, aku akuin.. tapi syukur alhamdulillah benar perkataan yang bilang usaha tidak akan mengkhianati hasil, melihat kalian sudah sebesar ini sekarang aku bener-bener senang dan lega.. we made it guys.. sekarang semua orang tau betapa berbakatnya, betapa luar biasanya kalian.. alhamdulillah.. dan aku yakin kalian akan tumbuh semakin besar kedepannya..

Seventeen.. Seungcheol, Jeonghan, Jisoo, Junhui, Soonyoung, Wonwoo, Jihoon, Minghao, Mingyu, Seokmin, Seungkwan, Hansol dan Chan.. adik-adik kesayangan kakak.. kakak tau kalian semua anak-anak yang baik, tetaplah jaga kekompakan kalian ya, selain kalian punya satu sama lain kalian juga punya Carat disini yang bakal selalu dukung kalian, jangan lupa untuk selalu pengertian satu sama lain, saling ngehargain satu sama lain, untuk selalu rendah hati, untuk selalu bersyukur, untuk selalu berjuang dan tidak menyerah, untuk istirahat yang cukup, inget untuk selalu jaga pola makan dan kesehatan kalian ya..
diusia grup kalian yang udah menginjak 6 tahun ini, kakak doain semoga kalian selalu sehat, panjang umur, semakin sukses karir dan percintaannya, semoga lancar dan dimudahkan semua urusan kalian ya, dan semoga kalian bahagia selalu.. aamiin

Sekali lagi, selamat ulang tahun yang ke-6 ya Seventeen.. 
*with so much love, your noona carat*

author: @Soreejillah
text:
Dear Seventeen,

Ever since I became a Carat just before Pretty U, I cannot even begin to explain the happiness you have provided me. Every album reminds me of different moments in my life, and so listening to you is like listening to the story of my young adult years. How do I write out just how much Seventeen means to me? I can feel it deep in my heart... it's like the same feeling you get when you hang out with your closest friends and you laugh and talk and forget about everything else for a while. It's a fuzzy feeling, a warm hug feeling. Seventeen's music gets me hyped on car rides, gets me in my feels when I'm sentimental, gets me comforted when I cry and gets me grinning from ear to ear when I'm happy. The sheer talent within Seventeen is bigger than Mt. Everest, it could fill up the whole ocean and there would still be some leftover. I am always, always proud to say I am a fan, a Carat. I wish I could say more, but the best words I can give to Seventeen is "thank you". I feel so blessed to be part of your journey. I support you and I care for you, I respect you and I love you. Thank you for shining bright for us, Seventeen. <3

text:
The things i learned after i slipped into the diamond life ğŸ’

S.copus: "jangan jadi orang egois"
(Di setiap moment s.coups pasti ngasi member yang lain dulu untuk berpendapat atau apapun itu, selalu mengutamakan grup dibanding dirinya sendiri)
_Best Leader

Jeonghan: "berani tampil beda, yang penting bisa bikin senang diri sendiri"
(Dia selalu nyari hal-hal yang bisa bikin dia senang kayak main lego sampe pelihara batu, meskipun orang bilang itu aneh tapi dia gak peduli yang penting dia senang dengan hal itu + perhatian walaupun usil)

Joshua: "sangat baik dalam mengontrol diri sendiri"
(Bayangin dia bisa gak pegang hp berhari2 bahkan dia bilang bisa bulanan, rata2 kita pasti gak bisa begitu + penyabar & gak mudah marah)

Jun: "walau tingkah dibilang bocah tapi pemikirannya dewasa banget"
(Selalu heran kalo Jun udah ngasi komentar di berbagai acara kayak tertata rapi gitu setiap kata yang diucapkan, cocok jadi temen curhat disamping kita dibercandain tapi kalau dia sudah ngomong pasti nyampe ke hati)

Hoshi: "sangat mencintai diri sendiri"
(Hoshi bisa sangat Percaya Diri seperti yang kita lihat pasti karena dia percaya banget sama dirinya sendiri klo dia pasti bisa, karena itu dia selalu bekerja keras. Bisa bikin orang-orang disekitarnya senang sama dia terus selalu bikin member yg lain semangat)

Wonwoo: "selalu berfikir sebelum berbuat"

author: @tyneola8137
text: i know everyone's comments here are their greetings and them reminiscing their memories. but id like to take this moment to say that SEVENTEEN NEVER FAILS to spoil their fans with songs either rare or have never been performed or if ever its been performed already, they always come up with a different version or put a twist to it. they dont repeat songs or latest title tracks over and over again not unless its for music show promotion and thats important, to listen and be aware of what your audience's lets say, "wishlists" or what the fan favorites are to keep them satisfied and keep them engaged and theyre doing that. also bc all of their discographies are worthy to be flexed and performed whether its for a special video, for a concert or whatever content it is. as long as theyre up for it and only probably a few artists (not that i know any other) are doing that cause mostly are just repeating their title tracks and some latest B-sides. also id like to point out how ALL of the members can sing so well despite, example, the hiphop unit, some of them probably prefer powerful rap or heavy music type of songs but theyre also good in ballads too. every member shined through and was able to showcase their individual range, character and color and the style of singing and when you put them together, it feels like a finished cake with icing and cherry on top. also i like how this sounds much better compared to their last performance of All My Love from SMA. their voices just kept improving and getting fuller. I already poured my heart so much in this one comment. nothing else to say here. I love SEVENTEEN so much and I knew I was going to be invested the moment I saw their Home Run performance from MAMA 2020. it was like love at first sight of that stage. If they indeed will still sign the contract. I hope I can stay as a carat til 2029. I would be almost in my 30s by that time.

text:
Hai, Seventeen
Aku salah satu Carats Indonesia

Selamat 6 tahunan cie dah bisa masuk sd xixixi

Ga ga ga ga kali ini serius

Hai, Seventeen
Aku salah satu Carats Indonesia

Awal aku kenal kalian tiba-tiba kalian nongol di twitter aku (Seventeen Tv), awalnya aku ga tertarik, tapi setelah itu kalian muncul lagi di beranda youtube aku lalu aku memutuskan nonton kalian. Dari masa trainee aku udah kagum sama kalian, tapi yg bikin paling suka adalah guyonan-guyonan, kehebohan dan moment-moment uwu kalian. Singkat cerita kalian udah debut dengan Adore U lalu Mansae dan tim dance coverku langsung coverin kalian, rasanya bangga banget. Beberapa tahun setelah kalian debut, kalian dateng buat konser ke Indonesia, aku udah beli tiket konser, udah beli tiket ke jakarta dan segala tetek bengeknya tapi aku gagal terbang ke jakarta karna ada prestasi yg harus aku kejar (lomba dance cover), maaf aku ga dateng hari itu tapi aku tau temen-temen caratku yg lain did a great job supporting u there at the venue. Proud of u Carats! Dan... ga kerasa udah 6 tahun aja umurnya, makin tua ya hahaha selamat menua bersama, Seventeen. Kalian semua ber-13 inspirasi aku, penyemangat aku, alasan aku bangkit dari keterpurukan, alasan aku lebih menghargai hidup, terima kasih banyak untuk kerja kerasnya, untuk pengorbanan kalian, untuk senyum dan tawa yg kalian lukis di wajah Carats, and thankyou for being Seventeen.

Happy 6th Anniversary.

author: @ayuannur9557
text:
The level of aesthetic in this video can't be ranked, really. 

I want to tell my own story about my journey as Carat too. 
The first time me and my sister met you guys was through a video Special stage] SEVENTEEN - girl group medley, ì„¸ë¸í‹´ - ê±¸ê·¸ë£¹ ë©”ë“¤ë¦¬ Show Music core 20160416 
Just because of you guys covered Gfriend's Rough in so manly ways that we started to feel curious.
We watched start from your predebut to debut stages, then watch the Weekly Idol and One Fine Day (though with OFD I feel sick and worried for you guys while watched all of it).
We slipped hardly into the diamond life after that. 
We first met at ICE BSD, Tangerang Selatan for you guys Diamond Edge's concert in 2017. My big brother and mother were there all the time. My mother and little sister fall so hard for DK and Joshua. I love Jun but always got wrecked by Dino (PLEDIS JUST RELEASE DINO'S SOLO PERFORMANCE ALREADY) and Woozi. and And since we saw you guys, my big brother always mentioned "THIS IS HOW MEN SUPPOSED TO PERFORM!" and always felt bitter if you guys got snatched in Award performances. We three siblings memorized all of your songs. My big brother who only loves games and computer the entire life would sulking if you guys are always the second. My little sister even printed out all of your best photos and spread it around her peers and friends, just to make you guys being much more popular. (Sssht, her friends all are NCTzen ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚) 
My mother poisoned our cousins and auntie too with the love for you guys, since my cousin worked on Shopee Indonesia and her boyfriend has a close relative who worked on Tokopedia, she got sick by frequently hearing (ahem sorry) BP and BTS. So even they got dragged and vocally active presented "How about SEVENTEEN?" to their superiors and supervisors ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ especially since it was around from Thanks era to Getting Closer. 
But they said Seventeen animo in Indonesia though its large, but nowhere near level BP and BTS, nor if they want it to be down to earth, near the level of Got7 and Gfriend. So darn frustrating! 

While me myself save my winning money from some poems and Indonesian Sastra competitions to bought your albums, while my mother bought the album of our family. My father even cant think of anything else except saying "No wonder, these boys are so handsome." 
I tried to drag my own friends. But most of them mostly Cassiopeia, Exo-L and Elf, while my best friend stanning SNSD. They still after all the years. 
My best friends from writing community and research friends then got dragged and love both DK and Woozi! I even joking with my friends about how I wait for your dating news, since I want to brag and be happy for your love too. 

We're so proud that we make them drink the most  beatifully contagious poisons called Seventeen. 

I love how Carats community are so chills and never ever faking or forcing they themselves to love you guys. Fake streams? Nope. We watched it repetitively just because we love how amazing the music, choreography, and content are, not just because we want to present "number of views". 

One day when I feel so sad and lonely, I cried so hard after listening to your guys Smile Flower and Us Again. I got cried again after I heard you guys recommend these two songs. You guys are here with me when I go to college, when I'm on the bus, my Mama singing along to you when she proceeded with surgery to relax herself, you guys were there when my big brother screaming fanchants while playing his games, you guys here for my little sister and me so we screamed cried laughing along side you guys too. You guys were there when I failed my college exams and long after that when  received my scholarship. You guys are here when I had my heart broken or when our most beloved cat, Ciel, sleeping loudly after hearing your song being played in the laptop. You guys are here for my family in the time we lost our most beloved cat too. You guys are here when me and my siblings were sad in the meantime Fairy Tail played their last "Snow Fairy, don't say goodbye!" 

Our words and love alone cannot ever convey how much we love you guys. â¤â¤â¤ğŸ˜­ğŸ˜­ğŸ˜­ We are incredibly sad since the pandemic cut our chance to meet again. We cursed it out with all of our heart but also feel thankful since you guys can take a rest, rest and appreciation that all of you deserve so much. 

You guys posted this within my birthday (23rd May) and my sister's birthday (28th May). You guys are within us too. 

Thank you for being born and meeting us! The best encounter ever we won't ever change with anything.

I won't ask for forever, but let's be together for a very long time.

Pengen cerita. Seventeen debut jaman aku kuliah. Dulu cuma tau mereka sekilas-sekilas aja. Sampe suatu siang temen ngenalin sama Dont wanna cry, aku bilang "ga ah ga suka Seventeen, kebanyakan orangnya, lagunya juga biasa aja, susah ngapalin wajahnya, kaga nemu yang cakep!". Tiba-tiba denger Check In di TV, kok enak. Penasaran denger lagi Pretty You, kok jadi semangat. Paling kepentok pas denger Home, kok berasa punya tempat, berasa disayang sekali. Ga keitung berapa kali muter Home. Mulai deh kucari tau mereka siapa. Aku jadi Carat jalur karma wkwkw.

Sampe akhirnya nemu clip Gose yang Mousebuster, aku yang ga suka nonton variety show, eh gara2 mereka sengklek aku jadi suka. Gose sekarang jadi tempat aku lari dari hari-hari yang kelam. Kalau sedih, kesepian rewatch Gose.

author: @hannahtang1308
text:
Dear Seventeen,
Thank you for being there for me these past 6 years. When you first debuted, your energy, freshness, and passion invigorated me, and just as I have grown throughout the years since then (going through college, graduating, working, now in medical school), it has been such a joy to see you all grow and mature as well. Thank you for capturing my youth and all the emotions that come with it: the bittersweetness, the sadness - but also the happiness and the excitement of it all. I've seen you beat all the odds, growing steadily over time, never losing your initial humility. Let's go a long way, Seventeen! Love you all! <3

(Iya lagi soalnya pas SD sempet suka tapi pas smp aku udh stop) dan yang dikenalin itu sebong. Di akhir bulan Februari 2018 aku diajak nonton MV DWC, thanks, clap, boom boom, dll, trus variety show, sampe isac tentang sebong juga, di situ aku gapaham apa apa tapi pas denger lagunya enak, asik, pokoknya pulang pulang ngepoin lagi sebong lewat gugel trus nontonin mv, video-video sebong deh.. sampe memutuskan jadi carat walaupun di 2020 an sempet ga terlalu ngikutin karena berasa lg down, tapi pas lg down gini sebong lewat lagi di sosmed dan akhirnya ketarik lagi... sebong ini jadi salah satu support system buat aku<3 aku ngerasa aku bisa lebih hargai diri sendiri hihi..
Kadang suka ngerasa nyesel kenapa ga kenal keluarga ini dari zaman tembok ijo gtu hehe, tapi gapapa aku mau menjaga yang sekarang aja sampe seterusnyaaaa{} 

Aku bahagia dan bersyukur bisa jadi salah satu anggota keluarga Seventeen Carats<3
Makasih udah lahir.. Aku sayang Seventeen Carats{}<3

dear sebong para abang-abanganku.
dari aku salah satu dari sekian juta penggemarmu.

meskipun presentase kalian baca ini 0.000..% dan gatau kalian bakal paham atau tidak apa yang aku omongin ini. but,

hai, aku carat sejak kalian memulai era adore u 2015. terima kasih kepada temanku yang saat itu mengenalkan kalian ke aku. mengenal kalian salah satu hal terbaik yang aku pilih. maafkan aku yang sempat sibuk dengan grup-grup lain, dan sedikit teralihkan dan tidak menemani penuh pertumbuhan kalian serta menemai luka kalian. tapi jujur, setiap comeback mendengarkan satu album kalian tidak pernah terlewatkanâ™¡, karena aku tidak akan melewatkan karya luar biasa kalian. karena mau sejauh apapun aku melangkah, tetap aku baliknya ke kalian-kalian lagi. karena kalian rumahku, dan fandom ini fandom pertamaku. you've brought me here, k-pop world.

salah satu hal baik pandemi yang membawa aku kembali ke kalian, terima kasih. terima kasih sudah menemani aku dikala sibuk dan penat dari tugas-tugas kuliah. membuatku tertawa walaupun fisik rasanya lelah dan butuh tidur luar biasa. terima kasih, seventeen. kalian salah satu alasan aku bisa tersenyum sampai saat ini. semoga tahun ini kalian semakin tumbuh dengan baik bersama caratâ™¡. reotranghaeâ™¡

today is my first time celebrating the anniversarry with you guys,i just want to say that I love you guys so much,you guys make my day brighter than before. text: Kenal kpop sekitar tahun 2010 waktu itu ditunjukin mv ring ding dong shinee sama temen dan saya jatuh cinta dan jadi kpopers ngak sehat -__- saya ngak suka boyband lain dan terkadang merendahkan sama seperti oknum kpopers jaman sekarang yg menghina semua group kecuali yg dia pilih maklum waktu itu saya masih kelas 7 smp. Tahun 2014 saya berusaha berhenti obsesi ke kpop demi kebaikan saya dan demi fokus menjalani SMA. Tapi tahun 2017 teman kuliah saya memperlihatkan dance practice seventeen nice ,yg waktu itu saya pikirkan adalah "gila penari latar nya kuat semua" dan "itu yg rambut panjang cakep :v" berawal dari ingin tahu jeonghan akhirnya saya terjatuh lagi ke dunia kpopers -__- dan menyukai seluruh member seventeen. Tapi alhamdulillah sekarang saya tidak membenci group lain bahkan sedih waktu got7 bubar

author: @Yasmin-ld8ev
text:
seventeen, nama yg selalu aku ikuti dari jaman2 seventeen project.
inget banget waktu itu lg bosen banget sama kpop. lagi fokus kelas 12 sma. fokus belajar terus tiap hari. temen dikit. kosong. terus kalian debut. menemani kelas 12ku yg semakin kesepian. membuat aku percaya gapapa buat fokus sama diri sendiri dulu biar bisa kuliah di tempat yg aku mau. aku selalu muter still lonely setiap hari menuju sbmptn. 4 jam belajar bener2 denger lagu itu aja biar tenang. selalu bilang gapapa kalau sendiri 

terus kuliah, gak dapet jurusan yg dimau. gak nyangka sampe drop mental di tahun pertama dan lagu kalian masih jadi penyelamat. terus sbmptn ulang, balik lagi bikin playlist lagu2 kalian dan tentu tetep balik ke still lonely. 

jaman2nya mencoba keluar dari toxic attachment di relationship, lagu fear keluar. aku jadi mikir. banyak sekali berfikir. dan akhirnya berdamai sama diri sendiri :)

sekarang lagi skripsian, aku udah jauh lebih baik dari dulu. walau capek harus magang di beberapa tempat sambil skripsi tapi selalu kehibur sama gose kalian tiap pekan. ngeliatin obrolan kalian di weverse aja udh bisa ngobatin rasa lelah kerja. apalagi puitisnya wonwoo atau peliharaannya jeonghanğŸ˜‚ oh iya, sekarang aku selalu dengerin together tiap skripsian loh! lagunya hangat banget. ngeyakinin aku bahwa aku akan terus bisa.

kita jalan terus bareng-bareng ya? meskipun nanti aku bakal lebih sibuk kerja, mungkin menikah, dan duniaku sendiri. meskipun nanti kalian bakal fokus individual project dan wajib militer. semoga kita selalu tetap bisa jalan beriringan. terima kasih sudah menolong aku di saat2 sulitku dengan musik kalian. selalu bersyukur bisa kenal kalian dan karya2nyaâ˜ºâ¤

author: @simpingforgyu
text:
to Seventeen and Carats,

Yesterday morning, I remember counting down for when it would be May 26th 12 AM KST. One of the first things I did was reach out to my online carat friends and wish us a happy anniversary, reminiscing on my friendships with them and how svt had brought us together. Then we start reminiscing on the past six years with svt and how much y'all have grown. Thank you, and I feel like thank you will never be enough to encapsulate all that I mean. But thank you so much for allowing us in your lives, for letting us watch you grow and to grow with you. Svt is home. I have never found anything else, let alone another group that makes me feel so at home, so warm. Your music feels like a hug, wrapping me with the warmth of the sun setting. I got so emotional reading y'all's post on weverse, listening to Carat's version of thank you for being born, I was crying all morning. We are so so proud of y'all. Please remember that we are always here to support you. Don't forget that you have one another, please cherish one another and the bond y'all have. Remember to take breaks (running itself is tough enough, but not running is an option too) and know we will always be waiting patiently. Thank you for letting us cherish you.

Happy six years, my loves.

author: @danarii_
text:
Dear: Seventeen

El 18 de Julio del 2017 conocÃ­ a 13 chicos que a pesar de no haberlos conocido desde su debut se han convertido en algo especial para mi, que me han ayudado desde tan larga distancia y que quiero proteger desde de la misma forma.

Han sido tantos los momentos que he vivido a su lado, momentos en los que he estado y en los que no, pero eso no evita que me sienta orgullosa y que me hicieran llorar de la misma forma que a todas, como por ejemplo cuando ganaron su firts Win con Pretty U o cuando sus familias les devolvieron sus anillos en seventeen proyect.

Adoro cada una voces, de sus palabras, de sus canciones. Cada uno de ellos son la razÃ³n por la que quiero estar viva, por la que lucho y me esfuerzo cada dÃ­a, y seguir apoyandolos con el hermoso nombre de carat es algo de lo que nunca me voy a arrepentir de por vida.

En algÃºn momento de mi vida mirarÃ© hacia atrÃ¡s, hacia mi pasado -que justo ahora es mi presente-, y cuando lo haga quiero estar orgullosa de haberme llamado Carat, estar feliz de haber crecido junto con ellos, de haber reÃ­do, disfrutado y adorado cada momento.

author: @Symphonyves
text:
My dearest Seventeen and Carats all over the world, 

Its been rough for me, especially recently, but i cant describe in words the amount of comfort and love i feel being in this fandom and supporting you. You all have matured so much and every time i think of how far you come, im moved to tears.

 You are all beautiful souls who have come to find a family with each other, i dont really have one so im very honoured and blessed to see all of you so close to each other. I love watching you guys and supporting you no matter what so please go at your own pace because i along with the many other carats out there will be waiting for you no matter what.

 We care for you and want you to be healthy as well as happy doing what you do. Im so happy to be a part of the carat fandom because watching you guys no matter what youre doing brings me so much happiness through such dark times. 

Thank you carats, thank you seventeen, all of you are special diamonds so lets keep supporting our boys together! â™¡

author: @nadiarafifah2348
text:
Liat carat pada nulis ucapan-ucapan buat seventeen, aku juga mau ikutan, hehe. 

Kenalin, aku baby carat, baru banget jadi carat 3 bulan yang lalu. Aku udah kenal mereka dari 2019 sebenernya, tapi baru stan sekarang. Nyesel bgt, kenapa ga stan dari dulu aja..
Eum, oke, udah cukup perkenalannya, hehe. 

Kalo di inget-inget lagi, aku stan mereka karena lagu Hug dan Going Seventeen. Lagu itu bener-bener nenangin aku pake banget. Waktu itu, aku stan mereka pas aku lagi kacau-kacaunya, terus tiba-tiba aku nemu playlist soft lagunya seventeen. Dengerin lagu-lagu mereka di playlist itu bikin tenang banget. Smile Flower, pinhweel, sama don't listen in secret juga bikin nangis banget. Nangisnya tuh karena lagunya tuh bisa banget bikin aku tenang dan ngelupain masalah aku. Emang ya, lagu seventeen tuh ga ada yg ga bagus, apa lagi lagu balad nyaã… ã…  

Ah iya, Going seventeen. Aku pertama kali nonton gose itu gose 2020 yang eps hantu itu, aku lupa eps berapaã… ã…  terus ketagihan. Eps fav aku itu don't lie 1 sama 2, TTT juga! Aku tiap nonton gose kaya langsung lupa sama masalah, dan langsung senyum, padahal baru intro doang. Ya.. walaupun lupa nya cuma sebentar, hehe. 
Udah, segitu aja ceritanya, udah panjang bgt, haha.

Terima kasih, Seventeen. Makasih karena udah bertahan sampai 6 tahun ini. Makasih karena udah nyiptain lagu-lagu yang bagus banget. Makasih, karena lagu-lagu kalian aku bisa bertahan sampe sekarang. Makasih banget udah bikin lagu-lagu yang selalu bisa bikin aku tenang. Makasih banget karena senyum kalian selalu bisa bikin suasana hati aku naik lagi. Dan juga, Terima kasih S.Coups karena udah jadi Leader yang sangat baik. Leader yang ga hanya sayang sama member, tapi juga sayang sama Carat. 

Aku gatau lagi harus nulis apa, karena rasa terima kasih dan rasa sayang aku ke kalian gabisa dijabarin satu-satu. 

Pokoknya Terima Kasih. Semoga kalian bisa bertahan sampe 10 tahun, atau 20 tahun kedepan. 

I really Love you guysâ£

text:
Dulu udah sering denger Seventeen, cuma males aja kayak apasih, ada unit unitan, males banget. Hi, Seventeen... Iâ€™m a Brazilian Carat, and I have so much to say to you guys! Well, Iâ€™ll try my best to translate my feelings to English hahaha... Well, now itâ€™s been like a year since I became a Carat (wow, itâ€™s already been so long??), and donâ€™t stan Seventeen earlier is one of my biggest regrets haha
You all came to my life in a really hard time and helped so much to go through it, and I fell so thankful that I canâ€™t put in words... I donâ€™t know if I would be here without you all :( 
I donâ€™t usually say that, but I love you guys. 
I have so much respect and admiration for your job; youâ€™re changing lives with your music! 
I just feel proud of everything Seventeen (and Carats! Haha) are reaching (?), please keep it up! I know thatâ€™s dark moments when you just wanna give up, and I say that by my own experience, but donâ€™t do that... Youâ€™ll always have Carats and each others. Youâ€™re music save lives, but donâ€™t risk yours for it.
Ok, sorry, itâ€™s came emotional. What Iâ€™m trying to say is: thank you so much for your hard work, and happy 6th anniversary! I hope so much moreâ€™ll come.

author: @elokdarazulisma1291
text:
Hallo Seventeen, 
Pada tahun debut kalian 2015 aku sempat menjadi orang yang menyukai banyak grup dan memasuki fandomnya termasuk kalian, namun perlahan aku meninggalkannya sampai april 2016 aku memutuskan untuk menjadi seorang CARAT semata, entah apa yang membuat diri ini kagum ke kalian aku tidak bisa menjelaskannya secara spesifik yang jelas di awal saat menonton sebuah acara musik aku menemukan sebuah kehangatan dan ketulusan waktu itu dari senyuman seorang S.COUPS ketika menatap ke kamera disitulah aku yakin untuk mendukung SEVENTEEN lebih lagi, lambat laun semakin dalam aku menyelam menjadi seorang CARAT aku tidak bisa keluar dan meninggalkan kalian terlalu nyaman diri ini mejadi bagian dari SEVENTEEN & CARAT
Terima kasih sudah menemani diri ini sampai sekarang kurang lebih 5 tahun 11 bulan, meski aku sedikit menyesal diawal tidak mengetahui kalian sejak tembok hijau, namun penyesalan itu lambat laun mulai tidak aku pikirkan lagi karena terlalu banyak rasa kasih sayang yang kalian berikan kepada carat sehingga aku dapat melupakannya, terima kasih selalu menjadi peneman diri ini ketika sedih maupun senang terutama menjadi peneman diriku dimalam hari waktu belajar ataupun mencatat materi kuliah... Kalian sudah ku anggap sebagai rumah kedua ku.

Semangat kesayangan CARAT Choi Seungcheol, Yoon Jeonghan , Hong Jisoo, Wen Junhui, Kwon Soonyoung, Jeon Wonwoo, Lee Jihoon, Lee Dokyeom, Kim Mingyu,  Xu Minghao, Boo Seungkwan, Chwe Hansol, Lee Chan, tetap menjadi SEVENTEEN yang selalu dibanggakan oleh diriku dan CARAT. 
Terima Kasih kalian telah berusaha keras sampai detik ini, jaga kesehatan kalian mari berjalan bersama - sama dalam jangka panjang. I Love U SEVENTEENğŸ¥°ğŸ’

author: @chaniehae
text:
Happy anniversary my happiness â¤
Ga terasa ya udah 6 tahun aja sekarang. Perasaan baru kemaren banget aku ngestan kalian. Baru kemaren banget jadi bagian dari carat. Eh tau taunya udah 4 kali aja aku ngerayain anniversary bareng kalian. â™¡
Eh iya, makasih ya udah hadir di hidupku. Agak nyesal sih ga ngikutin kalian dari awal banget, paling nggak dari kalian debut. Kata mereka ga ada kata terlambat untuk mencintai kalian, karena semua akan mencintai kalian disaat yang tepat. Tapi ga tau kenapa tetep aja gitu nyesel ga ngestan dari awal. â—â€¸â—Ÿ tapi yasudahlah. Yang penting aku sudah berada di tempat yang tepat, di fandom yang tepat dan mencintai orang yang tepat.
Oiya, makasih ya udah mengajarkan aku untuk lebih mencintai diriku sendiri meskipun aku belum bisa melakukannya dengan baik dan sempurna tapi makasih banget. Heheh.. Makasih udah buat aku merasa dicintai. Disaat aku merasa sendirian, kalian hadir dengan lagu lagu indah kalian. Disaat aku merasa tak ada seorangpun yang mencintaiku, kalian hadir dan membuatku merasa dicintai. Padahal kita belum pernah ketemu heheh.
Dan makasih juga udah ngebantuin aku keluar dari dunia yang gelap dengan karya karya kalian yang luar biasa. Dengan kekocakan kalian juga. Makasih udah nyuruh istirahat disaat lelah. Aku ga pernah menyadari pentingnya beristirahat sampai akhirnya kalian menyadari ku betapa pentingnya istirahat itu.
Tau ga sih kalian pernah nyelamatin hidupku cuma dengan lagu kalian? Wkwk. Lebay kan? Tapi emang bener. Aku masih disini karena kalian. Jadi teruslah berkarya dan menghibur banyak orang. Aku yakin ga cuma aku yang ngerasa kalau kalian itu penyelamat dan penyemangat setiap harinya. 

Sukses selalu dan mari sama sama melangkah ke depan dan meraih apa yang kita harapkan bersama.

Ga pinter ngerangkai kata kata aku tuh hiks. Tapi semoga ini nyampe di kalian meskipun bahasa yang ku pake ga kalian mengerti. Gapapa. Yang penting nyampe aja hehe.

author: @aiyukahan5858
text:
Dear SEVENTEEN, 
You guys came when I least expected it.. Never in my life I thought I would attached to these wonderful 13 guys.. "Love will always find a way" I guess it's true tho.  I heard about you guys few times even I met you few times earlier in Nuest "Face" and Hello Venus mv but I never thought all of you would gonna to be this important in my life.. During one breaking point in my life, you guys kept appeared around my surrounding till I finally paid attention to you guys.. At first I thought I wont be interested to you guys again after I watched Mansae mv then few months later I heard about you guys again.. I suddenly became interested to see your new song and I watched it, I like it.. I slowly became a fan.. I slowly catching up with your content.. I became curious then I found out how I actually have met you guys before in your senior mv.. It was shocking to me how you guys kept on coming yet I never really paid attention to you until the right moment; where I finally became a fan.. I felt addicted to you guys more than your music.. I only heard few songs but since the addiction is overwhelming and making me wanting more and more from you guys, I finally opened my heart to hear all songs in your album (which I never did this to any groups) Guess what? I felt so much regret of how I wasted so much time before.. Why didnt I stan you guys from the start? Didnt know you guys are this great in making music.. You guys really on the next level idol.. I found so much happiness in you guys.. Every small gesture from you guys hit me to the heart.. I feel loved and appreciated by how much you guys love us.. I love how our bond is strong, our relationship between idol and fan is healthy.. I love your positiveness and passion to be better and do what you like and live your moment to the fullest.. Thank you so much for coming to my life.. My youth is wonderful because I'm with SEVENTEEN.. Let's walk on the flowery path together.. Seranghae~ ğŸ’–

author: @rainsnoww9958
text:
Dear Seventeen
From one of carats

Sebenernya terdorong buat ini karena lihat komen2 banyak yg mencurahkan isi hatinya terkait sebong wkwk. 
Oke. Seventeen terimakasih karena kalian ada dan hadir di hidup aku, semua lagu yang kalian buat dan nyanyikan itu benar2 punya aura tersendiri yang bukan hanya sekedar lagu ataupun musik, karena aku bisa merasakan setiap emosi dan pesan yg ingin kalian sampaikan disana.

Seventeen, sekali lagi terimakasih karena kalian lahir di dunia ini. Keberadaan kalian membuat aku mengerti bahwa setiap orang memiliki potensi dan bakatnya. Terimakasih dengan segala keceriaan dan tawa yg kalian berikan kepada kami, sungguh dengan hal itu di hari yang lelah, hari yang membuatku terpuruk dan menyesali semuanya suara kalian saja pun sudah membuatku bahagia, apalagi tawa kalian. Nonton gose benar2 seperti salah satu kegiatan yang tidak pernah ingin kulewatkan, yaa karena melihat kalian seperti mencharge kembali energi yg tadinya sudah menghilang.

Seventeen, sekali lagi terimakasih. Teruslah berkarya dan menjadi motivasi untuk semua orang. Kalian berharga, i'll stay with you as always i can!!

*terimakasih juga untuk semua carat, kalian hebatt. Salah satu fandom yg memberikan kenyamanan tersendiri. Tetap ingat kita jangan sampai war karena seventeen tidak perlu hal itu. Uri sebong hanya butuh dukungan dan cinta kalian.
Dan terimakasih teman SMA ku yg sudah membiarkan aku ngeliat laptopnya trus tanpa sengaja ngeliat mv sebong yg mansae dan langsung jatuh hati sama s.coups. sampe kepo nontonin semua ofd 1,2 , svt project dll. Sampai sekarang masih ttp bisa mendengarkan semua karya Seventeen, sebuah grup dengan talent dan kebaikan hati yang memikat. Sekali lagi terimakasih.

author: @sayamcsu6733
text:
Selamat ulang tahun keenam Seventeen..

Dah lama rupanya duk dalam fandom ni. Kalau anak ni dah masuk tadika dah.. heee

Semoga tahun ini lebih baik dari tahun lepas dan tahun depan lebih baik dari tahun-tahun sebelumnya. Tak tahu nak cakap apa tapi Sebongie mesti faham kan Carat nak cakap apa. Betapa kitorang ni sayang giler kat korang. Teruskan menuju ke hadapan, kitorang akan tetap berada di belakang sokong korang, jalan sama-sama, jatuh bangun kami tetap sayang korang sampai bila-bila, dengan izin-Nya. Terima kasih sebab sentiasa menjadi buah hati pengeran jantung kami. Lepastu tak jemu-jemu duk suap macam-macam tak pernah tinggal. Jaga kesihatan, jaga SOP, InshaaAllah kalau ada jodoh tahun depan boleh jumpa lagi ramai-ramai. Sumpah tak pernah rasa menyesal suka korang. Tujuh belas sampai Tujuh Puluh. Dan selamanya.

Kepada carat, terima kasih kerana tetap ada dengan Seventeen. Mungkin kita sibuk, takde masa untuk diorang. Tapi tak bermakna kita tak sayang, kan. Betul tak?

Salam sayang dari Malaysia.

P/S: Semoga covid cepat hilang dan keadaan kembali macam biasa. Rindu giler nak berfanchant ramai-ramai masa konsert. Jaga diri!


Edited: Trans (cuz i think i should):

Happy 6th anniversary Seventeen.

Been so long in this fandom. If It was a baby, it must be in kindergarten right now. Heee

I wish this year is better than past years and next year will be a better year than previous years. I donâ€™t know what to say but Sebongie  must already know what we are going to say. How we love u so much. Keep going forward, we will always be there behind your back supporting you guys, walking together, either when you fall or rise, we will always love you forever, if He permits. Thank you for always became our sweethearts. And keep spoon feed us tirelessly with so many contents. Take care of your health, perhaps we will meet again soon. I swear I never regret love you guys. Seventeen till Seventy. And forever.

To Carats, thanks for always be there for them. We may be busy with our own life, sometimes no time to them. but it doesnâ€™t mean we dont love them right?

Love, Susu from Malaysia.

author: @jadev164
text:
My dear Seventeen,

I've been following your journey for 6 years already. It seems like yesterday when I first watched your debut MV for Adore U but 6 years have gone by already and both you and me have grown and changed so much since. 
I've seen you go from a rookie group with an uncertain future to one of the biggest, most popular and most respected group in the industry. Your creativity, your passion and resilience, your strong bond nurtured by consideration and respect for each other, all of those things have taught me a lot and helped navigate through the toughest moments of my life.
Through those 6 years you've given me comfort when I was tired, joy when I was sad and guidance when I was lost. Words are not enough to express how thankful I am for your existence. The only thing I can say is that, as long as there is a group called Seventeen, there will be me supporting and loving you.

Happy 6 years and cheers to many more years to come and even more success. I love you â¤ï¸

hai carat selamat anniversarry 6 tahun, untuk carat yang masih bertahan sampai titik ini, masih bersama dan mendukung seventeen makasih banyak :), jangan tinggalin seventeen ya carat. 
untuk seventeen makasih udah temenin 5 tahun 5 bulan dari masih smp sampai kuliah, terimakasih udah datang disaat yang tepat, saat udah lelah hidup, saat gapunya temen, saat dimana masa sekolah itu rasanya kayak neraka, saat masih males-malesan, saat satu keluarga ga ada waktu untuk peduli, saat sakit keras, saat pengen ngakhirin idup karena udah ngerasa worthless banget.

dan makasih udah jadi motivasi untuk merubah kehidupan, untuk start a whole new page, i'm now not the old me, but a new happy me. i proudly say that i'm no longer unsatisfied with my life, i cherished life more since i know seventeen. terimakasih seventeen udah menempuh dan membantu mencari jalan baru. maaf gabisa ngedukung 100% kayak dulu. i love my family seventeen-carats

I don't know how to feel about this, I feel like this should be carats message for seventeen. Im sorry our love isn't enough, I'm sorry this is all we could do to support you. If we could just give you everything you guys deserve, there's no doubt we will. You have become our healing, our pillar, our home. Listening to your songs feels like being consoled by a loved one, though you guys may not know each of us personally, but I know that the connection that seventeen and carats have is unbreakable.
It feels clichÃ© but there's no going back now, I will always be here to continue supporting you from afar. Let's reach new heights together, hand in hand in reaching our dreams.

All my love,
Carat

author: @nasywatsurayya9201
text:
ssup guys. aku juga mau ikutan cerita :D

awal tau seventeen gegara nonton mv mansae yang gak sengaja lewat dari yt, hapal banget sama warna rambut mingyu yg at first sight mirip ijo telor asin. gak lama, pas aku smp aku ketemu sama fina, my loafly bestie until now yang ngeracunin aku sama sebong sampai akhirnya aku diajak buat main ke tempat luar konser ode to you.

waktu itu aku baru aja abis di tinggal disband sama favorite boygroup ku yang dulu, istilahnya masih patah hati lah. dan begitu aku denger lagu hug, entah kenapa ada rasa bahwa seventeen itu bisa boygroup yang bisa bangkitin my happiness in kpop fangirling world. 

salah satu alasan utama aku nge stan mereka adalah karena vernon. pertama kali seumur hidup ku, aku nge fans dan jatuh cinta kepada idol ku gegara suaranya. vernon punya the way he rapping sendiri yang kalau di jelasin pake kata kata tuh susah banget. intinya dia berciri khas. dan setiap aku denge dia rapp atau nge vocal tuh selalu merding sendiri, kaya, suara dia semudah itu bikin orang jatuh cinta. dan pada akhirnya, di awal tahun kemarin aku mutusin buat stan mereka, slip into the diamond life, dan jadi carat sampai sekarang.

dulu, cita cita ku sendiri selalu di atur sama ortu. ortu pengen aku jadi apa, aku ikutin. ya namanya juga berkhidmat sih yaaa. tapi semenjak seventeen realease membership kit pilot and looked at them how gergeous theyre in pilot uniform, bikin aku kepikiran mau jadi pilot. aku pengen suatu saat bisa pake seragam yang sama kaya mereka. 

SEVENTEEN itu, selain kebahagiaan, juga alasan aku pengen punya masa depan yang cerah. i just want to tell you that, im glad to be a carat :D and, happy aniversarry my hapinnes~ lets being together for a long time, ya.

author: @bintangeu
text:
The comment section is so beautiful.
I have much to say but suddenly my mind became blank.
Thank you isn't enough to describe how much grateful I am to be a carat. Seventeen is like home to me. Even though maybe I was too late to join this fandom but still I feel so welcomed. Seventeen really healed me thru the pandemic. Now it's been like a year(?) since I started stanning them. Honestly saying, I've been a kpop stan since 2010 but seventeen really is something else. Maybe it's because I am older and more matured to know what love is. And yes seventeen is love. They meant everything to me. Thinking that this year is the sixth anniversary, made me thinking that will there be the seventh? God , I hate thinking about that but yeah I do thought about it. But no matter what will happen, carats will always stay with seventeen, supporting you guys in everything you guys did.
Till then, thank you so much for being with me when I was at my lowest, when there's no one with me. Thank you so much.
I love you guys so much.â™¡

author: @annorawal5168
text:
since everyone is writing comments in their own language and showing the diversity of carats and how there are carats from different parts of the world, I'll write something in my language too

mai bri khush hu ki mene seventeen to follow(mai stan ki jghe follow use kr rhi hou kyuki stan sbd shi nhi lgta hai) krna suru kiya, yeh meri zindagi ka sbse bra step hai jo maine ek dm shi liya. mai seventeen ko 2016 se jnti hou pr kbhi follow nhi kiya kyuki mai dusri group ki fan thi aur mujhe lgta tha ki mujhe bs unhi ko stan krna chahiye aur kisi ko nhi, pr mai glt thi, kaash mene seventeen ko suru se support kiya hota itne sme ignore krne ki jagah, kaash mai itni bri buddhu fan nhi hoti, pr abh jo ho gya voh ho gya, mai use change nhi kr skti, uski bajai mai inhe aur saalo saal tk support kr skti hou. mujhe suru se seventeen ka music accha lgta tha pr mere andr ye soch thi ki agr mai kisi aur group ko follow krungi toh mai apne pehle group ko dokha de rhi hou, iske baadjud mai seventeen ke songs jo bhut sunti thi. Toh seventeen ko 2 saal tk dekhne ke baad mene unhe follow krne ka socha, ye mere second group hai jinko mene follow kiya. mujhe lgta tha ki koi baat nhi, mai chahe kitne bhi groups ko follow kru mera first group hmase top pr rhega, pr nhi, mujhe pata bhi nhi chala aur seventeen achanak se top pr aa gya. Mai unko bs dekhti gyi aur dekhti gyi aur eventually voh mere top group bn gye. mene kbhi nhi sochta tha ki koi aur group mere top group banege pr yeh ho gya. mera support seventeen ke liya brta gya aur brta gya. mere phle group ki baat kre toh voh mere first kpop group the isliye mai bhut inexperienced thi aur mujhe lgta tha ki voh best hai even though mene kbhi dusre groups ko suna nhi tha. abh mai sbse first group ko follow nhi krti hou, unka music mujhe suit nhi hota pr mai thankful hou kyuki agr mene unhe kbhi follow nhi kiya hota toh mujhe seventeen ke bre mai kbhi pta nhi chlta. Seventeen ko follow krte hue yeh mera 3rd saal hai, intne time mai mene bhut sre groups ko follow krna suru kr diya hai aur mai ek kpop group bn chuki hou, pr ktine bhi group ko follow kro seventeen mera hmase top pr rheta hai, koi aur group mukje inti appeal aur khushi nhi deta hai, seventeen sbse pehla aur ek he group hai jisne esa kiya hai. time brta jaa rha hai aur abh kpop ka 4th gen aa chuka hai, mai ek amid and true 3rd gen stan hou aur mujhe 4th gen itni appeal nhi deta, abh bhut hi km groups hai jo mere taste ka music bnate hai, sbke ek hi jese concepts hai aur music bhi jadatar same concept ke hai, saath ma sbh performance aur dance pr jaada focus krte hai toh phir mere liye 4th gen groups ko stan krna muskil hai, jse jse time brega vse vse mera interest kpop se kam ho skta hai, mai ek 3rd gen stan hou aur mere saare groups jo jaate hue dekh bra bura lgta hai, mai itna jaada pyaar aur attention aur kisi gen ko nhi de paungi, pr ek cheez hmse same rhegi, mera pyaar seventeen ke liye. kitna bhi time ho jye mai seventeen ko kbhi nhi chorungi, chahe kucch bhi ho jye seventeen mere fav rhenge, till the last say the name and even after the last say the name, mai inhe support dete rhungi aur kbhi nhi chorne vli, seventeen is my happiness, unhone mujhe bhut sri chize sikhyi, aur mai iskilye bhut thankful hou, mai jese bhi ho ske inhe hmase support dungi, physical merch ke saath bhi, but sadly because of corona i can't, they aren't even being delivered to india, but still I'll support them digitally.
All my love to seventeen, please continue what you are doing, we all hope we stay together for a long time,
thankfully, sincerely 
from carats

author: @moviesbooksandmusic9458
text:
I really want to write a letter like the rest of these comments but don't really have a lot of time so I will keep it short.
Dear Seventeen

    Though you don't know who I am and I don't know ya'll personally. You make me feel as if I am loved by this amazingly talented, and supportive family. We all have struggles, some different, some the same. I haven't experienced a lot of things, and the future is scary, but after listing to your songs and watching ya'll, it made me think that even though there are so many uncertain things now and in the future if I am able to continue listening to music from Seventeen and whoever else, it's certain that I will have something to lean on and help bring me up when nothing else can. So many people say that they do it to make the people listing to their music happy and comfortable, but very few actually get that emotion and feeling across to me.Seventeen never fail to do just that. Seventeen you made me a better person inside and out. I thank you with as much sinceraty possible, I hope one day when I'm older and can make a lot of money, Seventeen will still be around and I will get to shower you with love. Even if Seventeen does one day disband, I will support everyone and will forever stand up for these amazing men. Even though it seems impossible to love someone you never met, I love you Seventeen and will continue to love you till the day I die.
              
                                                                        Love,
                                                         A non creepy fan, I realized I sounded kinda weird with the last line but I don't mean it like romantic love.

author: @yolaarindra1615
text:
I don't how to start this 'letter' to Seventeen. Should I start from when I stan them or why I love them? Well, I have known them from Home era. I was mesmerised by their triple barrel turn. I've been into K-pop from 2nd gen and it was the first time I see a group that can dance perfectly. From then on, I let them into my life. Even though I have been into k-pop for years, but it was the first time I wanted to stan a specific group.  I had always thought I was a multifan, but since I know them, I'm not. I never thought I want to buy an album or go to a concert, but now, I did, for Seventeen. It's really funny if I look back. 

They really change my life. I don't think I can remember how I was before I met Seventeen. . Now they are a part of my life. 

When I think about why I love them, I had already fallen for them. 
They are my youth.

Thank you. Let's be together from now on too. Love you.

author: @azkaarina7027
text:
Ini pertama kali banget komen di youtube. Liat carats indo pada rame ucap apresiasi buat cowo-cowo hebat ini. Selamat 6 tahunnya yaa my boys...
Tahun 2017, MV Pinwheel yg baru rilis menemukan jalannya di berandaku. Aku yg waktu itu lagi ngerasa berat tapi sok kuat gamau ngaku lagi susah. Meleleh air mata di part nya Woozi 
"ë¨¼ í›—ë‚  ë„ˆì—ê²Œ
ë¯¸ì•ˆí•˜ì§€ ì•Šê²Œ
ëŠ˜ ë‚œ ê¸°ë‹¤ë¦´ë˜ ê·¸ë˜
ê·¸ê²Œ ë” ë§˜ í¸í•´". 
Buat aku ngerasa bahwa ada yg nunggu aku melewati masa susah, mau seberapa banyak terjatuh. Dan kini aku bangga sama diriku yg bisa ngakuin overwhelming emotion kala itu. 
Beruntung banget dipertemukan kembali dengan Seventeen, yg buat aku nerima diriku sendiri dan gak nyerah hingga bisa sampai di saat ini.

Pinwheel, comfort song aku baik pas sedih, susah maupun bahagia. Pengingat kalo harus terus berjuang agar aku di masa depan gak menyesal dan kecewa pada diri sendiri. Belajar untuk nerima semua emosi yg aku rasakan baik positif atau negatif, apapun itu masih tetaplah aku. Penentram bahwa aku gak sendiri, pantas untuk bahagia dan semua akan baik-baik saja.

Buat temen2, ngakuin kalo kamu lagi gak apa2 itu juga salah satu bentuk self love. Jangan suka dipendem aja, you accept it and life will get better. 

Big love buat seventeen yg udh bersamaku di perjalanan self love ini.

Once again, happy anniversary!
