text: Annyeong, boys. Time flies, right? I remember the first time I saw you performing during Adore U era, well what can I say? It wasn't really love at the first sight but watching your live stages left a deep impression, because gosh who can resist a bunch of cute theater kids?! Not me because since then i began to do my own research, downloading your music to my drive then 20s got me hooked i kept playing it on repeat.. Though, i couldn't call myself a fan yet because it wasn't until Mansae that i realized no group made me feel the way you guys do, so yeah "In my eyes, it's only you, does anyone object?" [lyric from Mansae lol] and that pretty much sums up my discovery about your discography which becomes the beginning of this amazing delightful journey to better tomorrows with you. And it still amazes that All My Love for you since that moment never seems to lessen with each passing day, how is that possible? text:
Terimakasih SEVENTEEN!!!

Sebelumnya aku ngga pernah sebahagia ini buat suka sama penyanyi. Selama jadi kepopers dan ngikutin beberapa grup tapi ngga pernah sebahagia ini buat suka sama penyanyi. Bahagia banget bisa jadi carat, dulu inget banget pertama kali nonton seventeen waktu itu aku nonton MV don't wanna cry, dan mulai kepoin seventeen, member pertama yang paling dikenal Vernon karena bule, vernon jd first love ku di seventeen suka bonon mungkin karna gaya bonon pas ngerap lebih santuy. mereka talent banget nyanyi, dance, rap, produksi musik, produksi merch, jadi komedian pokoknya paket komplit. mereka bikin mood naik, pas lagi ada masalah terus liat mereka nyanyi apalagi liat gose jd lupa sama masalah ku. Aku fans dari tembok hijau. 6 tahun Anniversary untuk seventeen, tapi untuk aku 8 tahun sudah terlewat. 
Bangga banget kalau inget bagaimana perjuangan kalian untuk debut. 
Tapi ga bakal bohong ada perasaan khawatir menyelimuti saat kalian debut. Aku takut kalian ga dikenal publik dan aku pengen publik tau kalau kalian itu jauh lebih hebat dari yang mereka pikirkan.
Sampai akhirnya kalian jadi grup Kpop pertama dimana aku rela nabung berbulan-bulan untuk beli album. Album 17carat yg masih terpajang di lemari, dan sekarang nunggu album keluaran kalian yg terbaru. 
Walaupun sempet rest karna kesibukan kuliah, pada akhirnya aku balik lagi ke fandom ini. 

Terima kasih untuk tetap menjadi seventeen. Terima kasih sudah menemani masa-masa muda ku dan sekali lagi terima kasih karna lagu kalian selalu menolong ku disaat yg susah.

author: @sarirachas
text:
Dear Seventeen, Happy 6th Anniversary. I have gone on a roller coaster of emotions this year. Finding new emotions that I didn't even know existed in me. I can not express in words how much you've helped me this year. This one song helped me so much in my lowest time in life. It comforts me and I can not thank you enough for that. All the 13 of you made me laugh, cry, and... i dont know many emotions bare with me (^-^;) but you made me feel a lot.

Your music may not be in a language I understand but the emotions in them I do. And you're song made me cry (in a good way) when I thought I'd never cry for a song. It made me feel so many emotions and made me dance :]

You all deserve so much, so much more than the world could ever give, for the impact you've made on everyone.

All of seventeen brought me a new home, a beautiful home. Thank you seventeen for motivating me to live life again <3

Lagu2 kalian selalu berhasil buat aku setidaknya berpikir kalau semua akan baik-baik saja. Aku inget banget lagu pertama yang aku dengerin itu very nice dan mv pertama yang aku tonton dont wanna cry. waktu itu aku belum nge stan tapi dari awal aku udh ngerasa kalau kalian ini gak biasa dan akhirnya jd hardcore fans sampe sekarang. Aku gak pernah berpartisipasi banyak dan merasa kalau apa yg aku kasih gak akan cukup. Sama kayak lagu ini :)) Tapi y'all know what? apa yang kalian kasih utk carat selama ini udah lebih dari cukup. Carat cuma pengen kalian bahagia dan sama-sama sampe tua. So, if something doesn't come out right or the world goes against you just remember that we will always be there for you all. Thank you seventeen Kita sama-sama, ya <3

happy 6th anniversary, seventeen
may you always shine :)

author: @sevesthetic
text:
Hai sebong, seventeen.

Jujur dari dulu saya ga pernah tertarik sama k-pop, saya prefer anime dan jejepangan. Tapi begitu masuk sma, semua temenku itu k-popers jadi seiring waktu saya kebawa. Saya bner bner gatau apa apa ttg k-pop jd semua yg saya lihat dr temen saya stan. Iya, saya sempet jadi multifandom tapi belum jadi carat. Jujur, saya gabisa hafal anggotanya waktu itu, karena nama korea susah susah. Saya baru jadi carat waktu mv DWC rilis, iya 2017 dan saya nyesel. Padahal sama temen udh dikenalin dr 2015 tapi gak saya gubris, saya nyesel bgt. Soalnya dalam 2tahun itu banyak hal yg saya lewatin dari kalian. Saya jadi multifandom sampe lulus sma dan karena makin kesini sibuk sama kerjaan, pelan pelan saya jd ninggalin k-pop dan kembali ke anime (karena udh lepas dr temen sma juga jd gaada temen hype k-pop lagi). Semua fandom berhasil saya lepas tapi ternyata buat seventeen ga berhasil. Hiburan saya sekarang cuma bner" dari kalian sama anime. Kalian, orang" yang saya sayang lebih dari diri sendiri. Kalo bisa saya mau berterimakasih sama temen SMA saya yg sudah ngenalin svt ke saya. 

Dari dulu, sekarang ataupun nanti saya ga mau lepas kalian. Seventeen ttep satu satunya yg saya stan dari k-pop. Walaupun bukan boygrup yg saya stan pertama kali, tapi saya bisa pastiin kalo kalian jadi yang terakhir.

Untill the last saythename, i'll be there stand for you all. Beside you and always with you. Even if the world against you, i'll be carat forever.

Terimakasih banyak karena sudah hadir dihidup saya. Sampai saya tua nanti, saya pengen ceritain kalian ke anak cucu. Biar mereka tau seberarti apa seventeen dihidup saya. Sekali lagi, terimakasihâ¤ğŸ’ğŸ’

author: @defitaj.a2881
text:
Halo Seventeen, aku Catat dari Indonesia.

Seventeen, Pertama kali suka kalian itu di era Mansae. Aku yang posisi masih bocah waktu itu, langsung suka sama kalian. Ya, walau ngga terlalu ngikutin kalian karena blm punya hp sendiri waktu itu wkwkwk, cuma bisa ngandelin streaming MV pake hp ibu sambil ngumpet2. 

Aku mau minta maaf dan terimakasih sama kalin. Maaf karena aku sempat ninggalin kalian sebentar dan sibuk sama rl aku sampe ngedenger lagu kalian pun ngga. Tapi saat aku lagi terpuruk, jatuh banget, mental aku lagi sakit, kyknya lagu kalian itu kayak obat tersendiri buat aku. 

Kalian yang bener2 jadi penghibur buat aku. Saat aku bener2 tertekan karena harus menjalankan tugas sebagai pemimpin organisasi di sekolah, aku kyk liat Seungcheol mimpin Seventeen. Seungcheol sama Seventeen bnr2 kyk penyelamat aku disaat aku udah mau nyerah sama 'jabatan' dan label pemimpin di nama aku.

Dan sekarang, kondisi aku sudah sangat baik. Salahsatunya berkat kalian yang selalu bikin aku ketawa sama tingkah kalian.

Seventeen, makasih buat semuanya. Ayo kita bersama selamanya. Sehat selalu. Kami bakal selalu ada buat kalian. 

-ddef

Happy 6th anniversary! I am very proud of you all and I love you all so much! I canâ€™t be anymore happy than being part of your fandom, you guys sincerely made me very happy and feel loved. All youâ€™re Gose episodes are lots of fun and I always enjoy watching them. We would love to remind you all that we love you very much and will support you till the very end!

I remember when I first stanned you guys, it was when Hoshi, Minghao, Dino, and Jun visited I-land. I really found you four fun and have such a nice personality. I started to know more about the group and started listening to all your songs. I love them all! I can really tell that youâ€™re songs really has sentimental values and that thereâ€™s always a message in it that we all carats can understand and learn from it. You all made me happy and joyful, I seriously love all your laughs it is so cute and when you guys laugh you all make me laugh as well.

I will always be your supporter and I wish you all will succeed more in the future with all the hard work you all do. You are all very talented, so donâ€™t let hate affect you because no matter how much haters there are, us carats are more and will always be by your side giving you positivity, strength, love, and encouragement.<3

text:
Thank you seventeen for everything youve done for us carats. I havenâ€™t known this group for long but I immediately got pulled in when I watched one of your going episodes. Youâ€™ve become one of my people who lift me up when Iâ€™m sad or angry. Your songs are beautiful and have so much meaning and itâ€™s just such a pleasure to hear them. Thank you for all the time you guys spend to make us happy. Iâ€™m proud of yâ€™all and I canâ€™t wait to be here till them end because I promise you Iâ€™ll be here until the end and even after the end Iâ€™ll never stop being a carat until the day I die. Youâ€™ve made such an impact in my life and taught me many things through music. And you each individual taught me different things. 

Scoups - taught me how to be a strong leader 
Jeonghan - how to break gender standards where I live
Joshua - taught me how to be kind 
Jun - how to have fun and be silly in the moment
Hoshi - to be passionate about what I love 
Wonwoo- to find people/friends who help you get out your shell and speak up 
Woozi- taught me how to put emotions in things like lyric writing 
Dk- taught me how to smile and have fun 
Mingyu - 
Minghao - taught me better fashion and to be passionate about whatever your doing small or big or something you love 
Seungkwan - taught me how to make people laugh and also how to be sassy but most importantly he taught me to love my family more 
Vernon - taught me itâ€™s okay to be chill and relaxed and itâ€™s okay to be that way 
Dino- taught me to never give up and try your best to go down in history and make a name for yourself 

All of these things have made a huge impact on my life and how I am. Thatâ€™s itâ€™s okay to be the way I am and to find people who love me and help me become a better person. Everyday it might not be easy but knowing I can go home and listen to seventeen or watch their videos it makes my day 100 percent better then it started. Also as a carat I want you to know that other carats and I only want the best for you and to be yourself that we love the way you are personally and individually. That donâ€™t listen to the haters and stay strong donâ€™t go on diet because you think you need to look better donâ€™t change your person because you think you need to be better donâ€™t force yourself to do something for us because who ever you are each individually we love you for that and the uniqueness you all bring to the group real carats love you for any way you look act and are. So please never change that. I love you guys so much and you mean a lot to me so please stay healthy and strong and I hope one day I can attentive down your concert in real life and met the people I look up to. author: @bubblyu7928
text:
Dear Seventeen, 
Terimakasih selama ini kalian udh buat hari-hari ku selalu semangatt. Cerita sedikit, jadi awal aku tau sebong di tahun 2015 waktu mereka awal debut. Tapi, di tahun itu aku belum tertarik sama sekali sama dunia kpop. Tibalah suatu hari, aku liat mv sebong 'oh my!' aku jadi penasaran dan mulai ngestalk sebong. Mv 'boom boom' buat aku jatuh cinta bgt sama sebong dan mulai dari situ aku mulai ngikutin perkembangan sebong. Mungkin aku bisa dibilang bukan carat dari tembok ijo, tapi aku akan jadi carat sampai 'the last say the name' dan bakal dukung sebong terus karena emg udh sesayang itu sama mereka. Berapa kalipun aku oleng ke grup lain, tapi ga pernah tahan lama kaya sebong. Emg ya pelet sebong kuat bgt:') Terimakasih juga carat yang selalu apresiasi semua karya" sebong dan selalu support sesama fandom. Sehat-sehat terus yaa sebong dan carat! 
Love, 
Me who sincerely adore and love uğŸ’

author: @yustinaardena6477
text: Sebenernya SVT bukan grup kpop pertama yang aku kenal, tau, dan stan, tapi SVT grup kpop pertama yg bikin aku ngerasain seneng, sedih, asik, seru, heboh tiap nonton konten mereka(ğŸ˜‚). Bener bener baru banget jadi Carat jalur PSBB grgr corona. Di rumah doang jd diracunin SVT sm temen. MV pertama yang ditonton DWC dan bener bener bikin fall in love (asik). Bener bener lgsg naksir, dari situ ngepoin varshownya mereka sampe semua lagu dan tingkah mereka. Bener bener jadi nggak bisa keluar dari fandom ini, carat asik banget, adem, damai, seru, baik baik semua. Dan karena ngestan SVT, online class dan PSBB di rumah aja jadi jauh lebih asik dan seru. Semenjak ngestan SVT juga jadi punya banyak temen carat baru yang baik baik dan asik semuaa. Walo skrg tergolong baby carat, tp nanti (bbrp tahun kedepan) aku bakal tetep jadi carat yg bertransformasi jadi old carat buat para baby carat nantinya. Maksud aku, walau aku telat banget tau, kenal, dan suka sama mereka tapi aku bakal terus sama mereka di masa depan bareng semua carat yang sama kayak aku dengan tujuan yang tulus buat SVT. Happy 6th Anniversary SEVENTEEN dan terima kasih untuk semua carat yang udah bareng bareng sama SVT dari jaman tembok ijo ataupun buat yg baby carat (kyk aku) sampe sekarang, ayo bareng bareng lagi di tahun tahun kedepanâ¤â¤â¤

author: @ohvivi3083
text:
To: Seventeen and Carat Deull
INI CERITA DARI SUDUT PANDANG GUA YAH GUYS.. DAN JUGA INI GUA SUSAH CARA NGASIH TAU KEKALIAN NYA GIMANA... MOGA KALIAN NGGAK KAYAK GUA YAH

kenalin aku Alfie... aku mau bagi cerita sama kayak carat lainnya.... aku kenal Sebong itu udah lama dan udah sering juga denger lagu lagu Seventeen dan first mv yang aku tonton itu  ''Thanks'' dan variety show yang aku tonton itu Weekly Idol yang era Thanks, yang jaman Ujik kita jadi peri lemon wkwkkwk.... dan di era itu aku mulai tertarik dengan Seventeen dan aku inget banget disitu aku suka sama 3 orang Ujik, Babeh dan Mingyu.... tapi buat Mingyu aku suka nya ikut ikut doang (karena Kakak aku suka Mingyu).... tapi serius disaat itu aku kagum banget sama Seventeen karena sukses Dance (lupa nama nya) pokok nya Dance yang cepet lambat itu sama Random Dance, sumpah keren banget, aku sampek mikir '' kok bisa mereka dance kompak padahal member nya banyak banget'', tapi waktu aku memang udah tertarik tapi belum memutuskan menjadi Carat... dan singkat cerita waktu aku kelas 10 semester awal (mian kalo salah ) dan diwaktu itu juga Pledis itu di akuisis (?) sama Bighit, aku bingung dan cari tau kenapa tiba tiba Bighit gitu, dan setelah aku tau Pledis itu ent nya Seventeen... disitu aku seneng dong kaget dan keinget waktu dulu aku sempet tertarik sama Seventeen, jadi aku gak sengaja liat MV MV seventeen lainnya, dan dalam beberapa hari aku mau jadi Carat jadi Di IG aku banyak banget Follow Akun  Fansbase Seventeen dan carat... dan gak sengaja aku dapet Link GC disalah satu akun Fanbase nya Seventeen (lupa nama akun fansbase nya) trs aku Join, awal awal aku belum begitu akrab sama mereka semua, karena waktu itu aku lagi asik banget sama RP jadi aku lebih suka main RP..... sampai dimana pas rp aku sepi, aku mulai cari kesibukan dan nggak sengaja aku kepencet sama Notifikasi GC itu yang udah 12K an, iya serius! 12 ribu pesan sari GC itu, asal kalian tau itu adalah Gc paling rame sejagat raya, kalian tau 5 menit kita ninggalin Hp, tanpa kalian sadari kalian udah nabung 1K pesan.... dan saat aku udah mulai bosen dengan Rp dan bener bener berhenti main RP, aku baru sadar kalau anak anak Di Gc itu satu Frekuensi dengan aku, yang bacot dan suka rada rada gitu.... kalian pernah gak ngebayangin di suatu Gc fandom kalian itu, kalian bisa ngomong random, pap foto random, main game mapiah, VN tiap malam dalam satu waktu??? bisa dibayangin betapa ramenya Gc itu kan??... aku masih inget banget kenangan indah sama sahabat sahabat online ku itu, Kadal, Kanu, Aca, Ipi, nida, ndil, ayu, acer,michel Dlll kita itu paling berisik di Gc, sampai suatu malam Kadal buat Gc dengan anak anak yang dia anggap udah kenal banget (termasuk gua) disitu perlahan Gc utama rada sepi karena orang orang bacot udah Pw di Gc giba itu... awal nya kadal buat karena buat kick orang aja, tapi anak anak yg dia kick itu bikin Gc juga buat kick dia, jadi inti nya kita buat Gc baru dan Kick satu sama lain, sampai dimana Gc itu tiba tiba jadi Gc giba... dan kalian tau nggak sangking akrabnya, mereka tau sesuatu rahasia hidup gua yang bahkan sahabat RL gua itu gak ada yang tau... Jadi waktu itu pas Era Heng: grae itu datang disitu Juga Era dimana gua bener bener harus berusaha buat nggak Stres dan depresi karena KDRT... jadi gua itu besar dan tinggal di dusun plosok di Sumsel dan gua ada kesempatan buat Tinggal sama Kakak pertama gua di Serang Banten.. yahhh kalian tau bulan awal itu pasti semua orang belum menunjukan sifat asli mereka dan sampai dimana gua udah di tahun pertama gua tinggal sama mereka, so udah wajar kan seseorang nunjukin sifat asli mereka kalau udah 1 tahun tinggal satu rumah... DISINI GUA BAKALAN CERITA DI SUDUT PANDANG GUA JADI GUA GAK TAU KALAU DARI SUDUT PANDANG DIA ITU BAGAIMANA. YANG PASTI BAKALAN BEDA...... jadi ditahun pertama itu yahhh menurut gua sih masih wajar, seorang Kakak Ipar memaki adik ipar nya didepan ibu mertua nya sekaligus ibu kandung dari adik ipar dan istri nya, kalian tau nggak apa yg dia maki didepan ibu gua? apa? ''kurang ajar?'' ahhh itu mah biasa, tapi kalau '' SETAN, JIN DAJJAL, BABI, ANJING'' gimana? udah biasa tau luar biasa untuk seorang menantu laki laki yang berumur lebih 30 tahun memaki adik ipar nya didepan ibu mertua nya?.... kata makian itu memang tertuju khusus untuk gua yang sedang main sama anak anak nya, bahkan waktu itu juga dia pernah ngajarin anak nya buat ngatain gua ''PEMALAS''.... kalian pasti nanya kenapa dia bisa gitu? pasti ada sebapnya? iya dong masa nggak.. jadi singkat ceita yah.. kakak gua itu ternyata hamil diluar rahim, jadi kek janin nya itu nggak dirahim gitu, jadi dia harus dirawat dirumah sakit, so singkat cerita lagi, waktu itu gua pulang dari sekolah dan dirumah itu ada adik? temen? eh gak tau pokok nya kek temen tapi udah dianggap adik sendiri ama dia karena satu daerah... kita panggil Kak S aja yah... jadi kak S itu bilang kegua yang baru balik sekolah kalo Kakak J ( nama kakak ipar yang sangat baik hati itu:).... dia bilang kalau gua disuruh kerumah sakit (BTW rumah sakit nya kagak jauh) nah jadi gua kerumah sakit tuh TANPA NYAPU DAN NGEPEL DULU ( BTW gua itu seharusnya nyapu ngepel 2 kali sehari, pagi sebelum sekolah dan sore setelah balik sekolah tapi kalau sore kakak cewek gua gak sering nyapu pel duluan, karena takut lakinya balik trs rumah blm dipel atau di sapu karena gua belum balik sekolah) yoo balik kecerita!!... dan gua mikir kan ada Kakak S dan istrinya toh, dan gua kira dia bakalan pengertian buat gantiin gua untuk nyapu pel rumah selagi gua di rumah sakit... jadi gua ke RS tuh yah gantian jagain kakak gua yang sakit dan Kakak J itu balik tuh kerumah dan cuman ada emak, gua sama kakak gua tuh, sampai emak gua bilang kalau gua disuruh jagain kakak gua malem itu... sumpah demi apa gua kaget banget, gua disuruh jagain kakak gua satu malem dan sedangkan besok ada ujian, gua bilang dong kagak mau, dan mikir ''kenapa harus gua?'' padahal suaminya ada dan suami nya itu berangkat kerja lebih telat daripada gua berangkat sekolah.... singkat cerita lagi jadi mak gua mulai pegi dan gua? gua mulai nangis karena nggak mau.. jadi gua itu  nangis yahhhh lumayan lama lah yah, tanpa gua sadari kakak gua itu lagi telponan sama laki dia yahhh dan gua kira laki dia denger gua lagi nagis... jadi gak lama gua nangis suster Rs itu dateng dan bilang kakak gua udh boleh balik (kebetulan kali bukan?) jadi gua sama kakak gua itu mulai ngeringkes barang barang sampai dimana laki dia sekligus kakak ipar paling lemah lembut itudatang sama si Kakak S jemput... nah ini  nih bagian menarik, jadi pas dimobil gua udah berasa kagak enak nih ama situasi itu, trs tiba tiba kakak Ipar the best itu nyeletuk ''' ngapo kau dak galak kawani ayuk kau?'' dia tannya tuh dan gua diem aja trs dia lanjut tuh '' kalau dak galak ngawani itu dak usah dateng ke Rs'' nah udah aneh nih kan yak... trs trs dia itu kek nyeritain kalau dia yang nyapu pel rumah karena gua blm nyapu pel rumah, dah tuh dia mulai marah ngatain gua senggaja kerumah sakit uat kagak ngepel nyapu, padahal nggak begono yang terjadi sebenarnya... disitu gua balik nangis yahhh kalian tau kan kalo orang palembang itu ngomong aja keke ngegas apalagi kalo lagi marah plus jengkel.... disitu gua nangis sampai pas mau bayar parkir dia minta uang 2 ribu buat bayar parkir sama si istrinya buttttt si istrinya itu nggak punya uang kecil dan gua mengingat saat siang tadi gua beli Mie ayam sama kakak gua goput total 48 ribu dan gua ngasih 50k dan kebalian 2 rebu (kebetulan lagi bukan?) nah jadi awalnya gua berniat baik hati dan memberinya 2 rebu itu dia minta lagi trs karena gua kira dia minta 2 rebu lagi dan dengan polos gua jawab ''' dak kate lagi, ini 10 ribu duit sokongan '' ( btw pas disekolah itu tadi siang gua ada jam olah raga jadi minggu kemaren ibu guru itu ada bilang kolo disuruh bawa bola kasti  nah berhubung karena banyak kejadian diluar dugaan, gua lupa dan terpaksa hrs minjem bolah kekelas sebelah sam temen gua yg kagak bawa juga nahhh singkat cerita karena keasikan mukul bola gua kagak sengaja bikin tuh bola pecah, pecahnya sih nggak kek pecah yg pecah parah gitu, cuman kek beda aja rasanya dan juga bola nya emang yang jelek gitu bola temen temen gua juga banyak yang pecah karena disatu toko beli nya tpi yg beda toko nggak kok aman aman aja, nah jadi gua ama temen gua itu merasa bersalah dan mau gantiin besok jadi kita patungan 5k 5k tuh dan kenapa bisa kebawa? karena gua ke RS pakek celana olah raga dan gua juga niat nya mau sekalian beli bola ehhhh ternyata kagak kebeli).... nah dia marah tuh karena gua bilang itu bukan duit gua trs selama perjalanan kerumah, dia ngatain gua perhitungan, kagak tau malu dan bahkan bilang kalau gua kagak boleh tidur dirumah eh dikamar dia bilang buat tidur di teras, singkat cerita setelah masukin barang barang gua kekamar gua tuh nennangin diri gua sambil nutupin muka gua ama bantal, disitu gua lupa ada emak gua apa nggak jadi intinya dia ngomong gini '' nah kan nah ku bilang, ngapoi kau dikamar, kan dah ku suruh dito di luar sano, di teras'' trs bla bla dan diakhiri dengan '' katek malu!'' (kaga ada malu itu katanya).. nangis dong gua dan dipagi hari seperti biasa gua bangun jam 4 menghindari bertemu dengan dia pas beres beres trs pas gua dikamar buat ganti baju sekolah, disitu posisi nya dia udah bangun tuh yah... gua tuh udah tau kalau situasi begini tuh biasanya dia bakalan

author: @AR-vh9pe
text:
Dear SEVENTEEN,
         Thank you for everything. You may not know I exist, still, thank you. You helped me a lot. From focusing on my study, encouraging me to do more and to go far, and you all helped me when I am stressed and battling with my anxiety. You helped me by your music and its message. 
         I've been a Carat since August 25/26 last year, but I felt like I was in this diamond world for so long. I'm a bit down this month since there are so many bad things happening to me. But, I guess, I were just too lucky that I have your songs downloaded in my gadget, and can atleast understand some of it. 
         So, thank you, really, for everything. I hope I could see you all up close and have a proper conversation where we can understand each other's feelings and emotions. Help me more on the future, I'll help you too to reach the goal, together. 
          Again, thank you for everything. And, goodnight


- ^_^

author: @bajjj4056
text:
Honestly i was aware of them since seventeen tv era but didnt really pay much attention to them after debut. What finally made me slip and submerge right into the diamond life was, ironically, One Fine Day haha! From there i refamiliarized with them, and although sometimes i do pay more attention to other groups (being a multi is hard work lol), i dont think i'll ever stop being a carat. No matter what, I'll always come back to SVT because they're amazing, talented, genuine people. 

I dont think my adoration for SVT will ever fade away, even 20 years down the road. 20 years from now i'll still remember these 13 dorks or listen to their music and it'll put a smile on my face and a warmth in my heart.

So i guess i just wanted to say; Thank you for being such a big part of my youth, and thank you for being a part of all my love at this moment in my life.

Dear SVT, thank you for the last 6 years, and here's to many more to come!! ì¼€ëŸ¿í•´ ğŸ’™ğŸ’–ğŸ’

text:
Congratulations on your 6th Years Anniversary!

As of now, I can't believe, I mean that is as your loving CARAT, I don't know how to explain what I feel right now in knowing that you've been making music and preparing great choreography for almost (6) six years debuted the KPop Music Industry. I cannot imagine how many times you've been experiencing sleepless nights striving to create and prepare songs and performances a better one, a great one rather. From the moment I've heard your music, it was like a dimensional hole appeared, swept me up and slip me into the diamond life and never to return. I felt that everything inside me shift, in order for me to become part of your fandom. Also from that moment, I knew that you are the ones who gave a lot of happiness and inspirations to me. You were a sweet surprise I've never expected and the one I'll forever be grateful to know and to meet. Again HAPPY SEVENTEEN DAY!

author: @seventeenscharisma1589
text:
Mungkin ini bukan hanya sekedar pesan untuk anniversary kalian yang ke 6th, tapi pesan dari seorang Carat untuk Seventeen yang akan dia sayangi hingga kapanpun. Aku tidak bisa merangkai kata untuk mengungkapkan perasaanku kepada Sebong dengan singkat, karna rasa ini terlalu penuh akan kebahagiaan dan rasa syukur yang telah kalian berikan. Aku sangat mencintai kalian. Walau pesan ini akan sulit tersampaikan, namun diriku tak pernah lelah untuk mengungkapkannya.
Seventeen, terimakasih sudah hadir di hidupku, terimakasih telah memberiku banyak sekali kebahagiaan, terimakasih telah mengajariku banyak hal tentang menghargai orang lain, aku banyak belajar hal-hal yang tidak pernah aku dapatkan sebelum aku mencintai kalian. Jika orang bertanya padaku mengapa aku sangat mencintai kalian, aku akan menjawab, "Karna Seventeen benar-benar telah mengajariku tentang apa yang disebut dengan 'Cinta, Kebaikan, dan Ketulusan' ". Aku mencintai kalian.
Jangan pernah khawatir tentang hubungan kita, aku percaya kita pasti akan saling mencintai selamanya, kita akan tetap berada di keluarga Seventeen Carats selamanya, meskipun kita masih belum tahu jalan kita di masa depan.  Namun, percayalah, Kami akan melindungi kalian dari semua kesedihan dan jalan yang melelahkan ini karena kami Mencintaimu.
Aku berharap suatu hari nanti dapat bertemu kalian, aku ingin mengatakan secara langsung pada kalian bahwa aku mencintai kalian. Aku selalu berdoa yang terbaik untuk kalian. Aku sangat Mencintai Kalian!â™¡

author: @kwxnhooniee
text:
It's been 6 years already.... But most of us know them as much as all those years we've spent not knowing them.. SEVENTEEN, our home, our safe place. Someone who understands you more than anyone could... Someone we feel safe with. Someone we would love and support for our entire lives. Even if they don't remain as a grp somewhere in future, they'll all be the same 13 in our heart. Forever. They may not know that a person like you exist, but they know you as carats. They love you. A lot! They convey it to us thorough songs if words may not be possible..Let's  one proud to be carats and have our boys with us... I shouldnt be getting emotional on a day like this, but ik we can't resist it. Tears may fall off, but that's the tear of all those feelings, all those love you have for them. They've come all the way after the struggles they had to go through. For us... I couldn't include what all I wanted to say, but I want to end with a Thank you note...
To SEVENTEEN,
Thank you. Thank you for always bringing all those stupid smiles on our face. Thank you for always being by our side. Thank you for being our home, our safe place. Thank you for all those hard work you've done for us... Thank you for being our cute crackeheads. Hehe. Thank you for every single thing you've done for all of us carats... Always remebr that we WERE with you, IS with you and will ALWAYS be with you throughout, no matter what!
 We love you a lot.....
By, A carat

author: @chaniepcc8510
text:
HAPPY 6TH ANNIVERSARY SEVENTEEN
SEVENTEEN, THANK YOU FOR EVERYTHING, I WILL ALWAYS BE CARAT AND SUPPORT YOU, I PROMISE

Oke, mau ikutan juga bikin surat pendek utk SEVENTEEN..
Mungkin aku tidak mengikuti kalian dari awal dan baru-baru mengenal kalian sekitar 1,5 tahun terakhir ini tapi terima kasih untuk semuanya. Karena kalian, aku jadi kembali ke dunia kpop lagi. Karena kalian, seperti ada alasan dan harapan setiap bangun di pagi hari apalagi di masa-masa sekarang ketika bahkan sulit untuk bertemu teman di real life. Personally, banyak hal terjadi di 2020 dan SEVENTEEN adalah salah satu alasan kenapa aku masih bisa bertahan sampai sejauh ini. 
Percayalah, aku sudah mengenal kpop dari 2011 dan beberapa kali berganti fandom, tapi baru kali ini benar-benar merasa sayang banget dengan group kpop dan merasa sedekat itu dengan kalian, SEVENTEEN dan CARATS, walaupun sebenarnya kalian jauh. I believe that SEVENTEEN and CARATS will always be together, forever. Aamiin.

SEVENTEEN, once again THANK YOU for your music, your content, your personality, your smile and your everything. As Woozi said : "I want to do these forever with this people". Yes, please, do it forever and always be together as SEVENTEEN. We, CARATS, also want to do this forever with you, SEVENTEEN :)

author: @ciciokta
text:
Hai Seventeen, nggak kerasa udah 6th kalian debut dan udah 4th aku nge stan kalian. Sebelum "kenal" kalian, aku ga pernah yang namanya fall into a kpop group that much as much as I fall into you guys. Apa ya... kayak ngerasa klik aja gitu sama kalian. Meskipun kita jauh dan mungkin kalian ga pernah tau kalo ada aku yang ngedukung kalian, tapi aku ngerasanya kayak kita deket banget dan kita itu temen sekaligus keluarga.
Inget banget waktu pertama kali dengerin lagu clap di salah satu platform music secara ga sengaja pas lagi perjalanan mau bimbingan skripsi, terus ngerasa addicted sama partnya vernon, and then penasaran dan voilaaa jadilah aku yang sekarang gabisa jauh-jauh sama kalian. Terimakasih banyak karena kalian udah nemenin aku di masa-masa susah maupun senangku. 
Aku sadar, aku gabisa ngasih banyak ke kalian. Tapi satu hal yang aku bisa jamin, aku bakalan terus dukung kalian, sampai kapanpun.
Semoga kalian sehat dan bahagia, semoga kalian bisa mencapai apapun yang kalian inginkan, dan mari kita sama-sama dalam waktu yang lama. 
Aku sayang kalian.
I love you Seventeen, forever.

Eventhough, I'm really late stanning from 2020 during Henggarae Era, I'm really happy that I am able found you guys, the group that always bring cheerful, happiness, fun, and smile to each of our faces to all of Carats around the world wherever you are. It may be hard that I quite miss many moments from the previous years, but I'm happy that now I am able to celebrate today 6th Seventeen's anniversary for the very first time. Thank you for always working hard, giving the very best, and giving happiness. Take care, stay healthy and safe. Im glad to know each and one of you, through your songs from different album, through many different contents to bring back my happiness and laughters from many sadness, dark and sorrow moments. Thank you once again, and HAPPY 6th ANNIVERSARY SEVENTEEN!!!

Jujur aku baru ngikutin kalian, yang bener bener sampe akhirnya jadi Carat itu tahun 2020 kemarin. author: @yuikorj96
text:
May 26, 2021

Dearest sebongies,

When I saw you guys for the first time - in that Manse Dance Practice Video a few years ago,  I thought you were just some other groups I could stan for a while and then leave, but no. Coincidentally, you were with me in the most stressful times of my life - my last three years in college, when I couldn't get my diploma on time, when i was losing and when i lost my dad and now, you are still with me during - probably - the most anxious chapter in my career.

Thank you so much from the bottom of my heart. You might not know there is a me that exists in the world but I know how much you love your carats and fortunately I am one of them. I haven't felt being loved and this strong of a connection towards an artist for a long time. Thank you. I feel like with you, I am always loved, heard and comforted.

I thank God for leading me to you in the most, darkest times in my life. You are one of the greatest gifts I have ever received. Thank you so much. I hope to be with you for more years to come and I pray that you guys find your own happiness as well. We love you. I love you, so, so, much.

xoxo,
Rej

text:
Annyeong seventeen. From carat indonesia.
Awal aku kenal kalian mungkin sekitar tahun 2018 . Awalnya karena waktu itu aku mmg pengen STAN suatu grup. MV pertama ku very nice , mulai tertarik karena lagu clap. awalnya ngak tau kalo itu lagu CLAP soalnya sering denger gegara dibikin misherad lyric. Lalu yg bikin aku fall in love to sebong adalah lagu left and right dan don't wanna cry. Jujur kirain lagu kalian itu biasa aja . Tapi setelah aku kepoin kalian itu semakin bikin aku senang.dari liriknya banyak hal yg dapat diambil. Bisa didengarkan kapan pun. Terutama ketika aku sedang murung. Awalnya juga ngak yakin jadi carat soalnya disekitar ku jarang ada carat yg benerÂ² carat. Tapi karena Corona , jadi aku lebih banyak punya teman carat walaupun itu online tapi aku ngak kesepian lagi. 
Dulu pas bosan aku bisa stres.semenjak STAN svt aku bisa nonton gose, streaming MV. Bukan cmn ketenangan , bisa bikin ketawa, buat motivasi tapi itu juga biar bantu svt . Wish moga kalian sehat selalu dan makin sukses. Walaupun aku baru kepoin kalian tahun 2020 tapi aku senang!. Ngak tau mau hilang apa lagi. 
Thanks seventeen .thanks  can make things that make me excited. Good luck always.
Thanks!

author: @10daniyahmarsha98
text:
Untuk Seventeen di tempat.

Apa Kabar Seventeen? Akhir-akhiran ini sudah mau musim panas, jangan keseringan minum es.

Seventeen, kalian sangat penting seperti huruf p dalam kata raspberry, sangat dinantikan seperti sidang saat akhir semester, dan sangat menenangkan seperti lagu Smile Flower.

Ketahuilah, diatas lara masih ada harsa, saat tidak ada kupu-kupu yang membantu bunga untuk penyerbukan masih ada angin, saat tak ada yang bisa jadi sandaran masih ada CARAT yang dapat kamu andalkan.

Terima kasih sudah menemani sampai sekarang, terima kasih karena sudah mengisi masa mudaku. Mari bertemu di atas bianglala tanpa nestapa. 

Say The Name, Seventeen! Terima Kasih

Dari Daniyah, ditulis di atas meja sambil memegang pena (Indonesia, 2021.05.26)

I still remember accidentally clicking Adore U and directly falling in love. I've been a K-Pop fan since 2010, and out of all fandoms I've been in, I've been a Carat for the longest time (almost 6 years now). author: @_k.ahyeon_
text: I can't believe it has been 6 years since you guys debuted. Even though this is my first anniversary with Seventeen, I have some things I would like to say. For the past year, I really started to get into Seventeen and now they are my ult group. I got to learn the personalities and special talents of individual members. I was exposed to kind words and beautiful songs and beautiful, synchronized choreographies. I was blessed with music videos and group pictures and selcas. I did not think I would come so far being a Carat. Thank you Seventeen. You helped me at my lowest, made me feel happiness and cared for us Carats as a whole. You gave us all your efforts and showed us all of your amazing talents that we can never forget. You showed us love. In the future, let's continue to support one another and become stronger by each other's side. I love you so much. Happy 6th Anniversary <3

text:
Every anniversary, i'm always so grateful and emotional that I met them but damn, this year hits different coz I'm going 2nd year in college and the hyung line will soon go and serve in the military...

I'm a little bit fearful for the future, had thoughts that what if SVT disbands when they reach the end of their contract?! What if they won't renew it? I've literally aged together with them and i'm really thankful that they helped me go through hard times in highschool.

But ya know, i've come up into a realization. We don't know what the future holds, that's for a fact but what we do know is no matter what happens...

*CARATS WILL ALWAYS HAVE SEVENTEEN AND SEVENTEEN WILL AWALYS HAVE CARATS* !!!! 

so since we all have this time left, we should really cherish each moment, support them and  help them in promoting their songs.

I aged together with Seventeen and i'm 100% sure that i'm going to stan them beyond my youth, hell imma be a carat till im 70!!! That's my story!!!
#6yearswithSeventeen #AllmyLove

author: @gezellight3814
text:
Aku memang enggak kenal sama sebong dari jaman tembok hijau. 
Aku kenal sebong dari masih pake rok biru, kayaknya waktu itu sekitar tahun 2016, awal" diracunin K-Pop sama temen. Awalnya dikenalin sama grup lain, cuma akhirnya nemu sebong, dan aku mulai dari nonton mv mansae sama nonton OFD yeosodo.
Lanjut ke masa putih abu, aku mulai sering oleng ke grup lain. Sampe bingung aku tuh sebenernya masuk fandom mana, lol bgt. Tapi, setiap kali ditanya "kamu suka grup ap? Fandom mana?" Aku selalu PD bilang, "aku Carat, fansnya Seventeen" padahal sebenernya waktu itu aku banyak banget ninggalin update sebong, dan lebih condong ke grup lain, lol. Ngerasa jadi carat KTP, ngerasa berkhianat gitu.
Tapi, biarpun sering oleng ke grup lain, ujung"nya aku bakal bosen, jujur cepet bosen, bukan berarti grup lain ngebosenin ya, cuma... kebanyakan lagu" grup lain itu enggak sesuai sama selera musik aku. Konten"nya juga, cara ngelawaknya juga, kayak kurang konek, nggak sefrekuensi.
Ujung"nya aku balik lagi ke sebong. Always. Mereka bener" kayak rumah buat aku.
Sampe lulus masa putih abu aku masih sering oleng, balik, oleng, balik.
Nah, pas 2020, mulai pandemi. Makin bosen lh aku sama dunia K-Pop. 
Tapi sebong selalu dateng lagi, fresh, dan bikin aku senyaman dan sebahagia itu. 
Tahun 2020, aku selalu ikut update sebong, dan bener" ngerasa di-spoil. Enggak bosen lagi, bener" SVT saved my 2020. Dan akhirnya aku sadar, bisa"nya aku oleng ke grup lain dan gak setia sama sebong... padahal aku sadar bgt kalo mereka itu my  home, aku seneng sama lagu"nya mvnya, kekeluargaan mereka. 
2020, aku mutusin buat stan sebong only, they're my ultimate. My best. Grup lain cuma lirik bentar doang, respect keberadaannya, udah. My heart will always be with SVT & carat.
And guess what, i feel like being loyal to only SVT is the best desicion ever. 
Rasanya dunia cuma milik kita (carat) sama sebong doang, udah, bahagia bgt.
Makasih banyak buat sebong & carat, udah jadi rumah buat aku. Selalu bikin aku nyaman, dan motivated. You guys, really radiating youthful energy, being with this family make me always feel like i'm forever 17 y.o. 
Aku seneng dan terinspirasi bgt sama S.coups yg makin tua makin cheerful, sama jeonghan yg selalu iseng sama org" tersayangnya, sama joshua yg selalu gentle, sama jun yg selalu sweet, sama hoshi yg selalu bisa bangkit, sama wonu yg gk berubah" lol, sama uji yg selalu hardworking, sama the8 yg makin bijak dan estetik, sama mingyu yg selalu think positively, yg sering bilang ke carat buat mencoba apapun yg kita mau, sama dk yg selalu improve and  put his best effort on everything, sama uri boo yg selalu semangat ceria, ramah, sama vernon yg selalu stay cool dan selalu bilang ke kita buat jgn peduli sama standar org lain, dan buat dino yg ngebuktiin kalau selama kita terus berusaha, kita bakalan jadi lebih baik dari sebelumnya. 
Thank you so so much.

author: @hasnamahitsa9519
text:
Kalo gue ngga kenal svt pasti hidup gue bakal tambah datar dan suram. Tambah jarang ketawa, tambah sering stress, dll. Tapi gara gara kalian, hidup gue jadi berwarna. Ngakak mulu, mood banget pokoknya. Hp gue jadi ada gunanya, gpp walau memori penuh, kuota habis, yg penting ada tujuan dari penuh dan habisnya memori dan kuota gue. 

Sayang bgt sama kalian, bukan jenis sayang ke pacar, keluarga atau sahabat. Beda, ngga bisa dijelasin rasa sayang gue ke kalian tuh kaya gimana. Pokoknya kalian punya tempat sendiri di hati gue. Svt adalah bagian dari hidup yg ngga bakal gue lupain sampai tua nanti. Meski kalian udh ngga aktif, meski suatu saat gue udh ngga bisa ngefangirl, kalian bakal gue inget sebagai salah satu kenangan paling membahagiakan. 

Janji.

author: @Margareta_Wulandari
text:
Dear SEVENTEEN
Mulai suka 13 manusia absurd ini sejak kalian tampil di weekly idol era "Thanks" Pertama liat ga tau gimana langsung suka banget sama kalian.
Tarian kalian yang keren banget, suara kalian yang unik banget, bahkan kalian juga lawak banget. 
Aku cuman mau bilang terimakasih banyak. Untuk semua yang kalian kasih ke Carat. Gak pernah ada dibayanganku hubungan idol dengan fans sedekat ini. Bahkan aku belum berkesempatan bertemu kalian, tapi aku bisa merasakan kedekatan kalian. 
Kalau liat macan aku ingat Hoshi, kalo liat nasi inget Woozi, kalo liat cherry inget S.Coups, dan masih banyak lagi. Terimakasih sekali lagi untuk selalu memberikan yang terbaik untuk kita para Carats
We love you guys so much:)))

author: @alsawidyad9982
text:
Untuk kamu, 13 pria yg berjuang dari 0.
Terimakasih atas kerja keras kalian, dan semua waktu, tenaga, pikiran yang kalian curahkan sampai saat ini
Terimakasih untuk tidak pernah menyerah dan terus berjuang bersama
Pasti hal yang sangat sulit untuk meninggalkan kampung halaman, keluarga, teman dan semua kenangan untuk mengejar mimpi kalian
Aku hanya ingin mengatakan kepada kalian, selamat kamu sudah melewati banyak hak yang tentu saja tidak mudah.
Aku percaya semua yang kalian korbankan  selama ini bukan hal yang sia-sua
Aku percaya bahwa mereka akan bangga dengan kerja keras dan pencapaian kalian, kalian semua sudah bekerja keras lebih dari apapun
Kami, carat, berjanji untuk selalu berjalan mendampingi kalian agar kalian tidak pernah merasa sendiri dan kesepian
kami berjanji tidak akan pernah meninggaljan kalian, meskipun harus melalui hujan dan badai, kerikil dan batu, atau apapun itu
Mari selalu bergandengan tangan untuk kedepannya, 
Mari mengejar mimpi kita bersama sama
Mari terus bersama sampai rambut kita berubah warna menjadi abus
Kami berjanji bahwa kamibjuga akan bekerja keras untuk menjadi carats yg bisa SVT banggakan, sama seperti SVT yang selalu dengan bangganya mengatakan bahwa kalian sangat senang memiliki kami.
Terimakasih kami rasanya tidak cukup untuk membalas cinta dan kerja keras kalian, tapi tetap, aku ingin menyampaikan rasa syukur dan terimakasih kepada kalian yg sudah hadir dalam hidup kami dengan membawa kebahagiaan, tawa, dan kenangan indah. Terimakasih sudah menjadi penyembuh kami dengan semua canda tawa, musik, dan dan kata kata hangat kalian kepada kami. Mari selalu bersama untuk menciptakan kenangan indah lainnya untuk masa muda kita. Happy Anniversary SEVENTEEN, selalu bahagia dan sehat selalu!

To SEVENTEEN with love,

You've come through a long way! I'm so proud of you! Just so you know, I'm more than proud being Carat! No beautiful words can describe how much I'm thankful being part of Seventeen's life even tho we're thousands of miles apart. 

Happy 6th Anniversary! Thank you so much, I love you so much. Tbh, I'm so proud and happy that I don't know what to say anymore. All I know is I love you so much guys and I'm so grateful of you. Please, keep walking. No need for us to rush, we just need to stay, support and be happy with each for lifetime. I promise I'll be there through ups and downs. You saved me, so, I will always be thankful of you and will love you 'til no end, my life long idols. 

Loving you 'til no end,

Rgn

author: @etikaard
text:
Hi, SEVENTEEN! Glad to know you, boys!
Banyak hal yang ingin ku sampaikan pada kalian, tapi karena aku tak pandai merangkai kata-kata, jadi aku akan menyampaikan secukupnya saja. 
1. TERIMA KASIH telah hadir menemani hidupku dan hidup CARATS disana. 
2. TERIMA KASIH telah membuatku merasa menjadi orang yang special, mungkin CARATS lain juga begitu.
3. TERIMA KASIH telah menyadarkanku untuk menjadi seseorang yang lebih dewasa dalam menghadapi permasalahan di dunia ini.
4. TERIMA KASIH telah menyemangati hari-hariku dan CARATS dengan karya-karya yang begitu luar biasa.
5. TERIMA KASIH telah menganggap CARATS sebagai teman, keluarga, atau pendengar. Hal itu sangat bermakna bagi kita.
6. TERIMA KASIH telah menyebarkan positive vibes terutama di era pandemi ini.
7. TERIMA KASIH telah menciptakan sesuatu yang luar biasa dan unik.
8. TERIMA KASIH selalu menampilkan sesuatu yang berbeda di tiap penampilan kalian.
9. TERIMA KASIH telah berjuang dan bertahan sejak awal hingga saat ini.
10. TERIMA KASIH karena selalu bersama-sama.
Aku harap kalian selalu bahagia seperti bahagia CARATS ketika kalian hibur. Aku harap kedepannya kalian akan menemukan seseorang yang mengerti kalian dengan baik. INTINYA KALIAN HARUS BAHAGIA, CARATS JUGA HARUS BAHAGIA YA. 

HAPPY 6TH ANNIVERSARY, SEVENTEEN! 

Astaga seperti menulis essay. Semoga ga keciduk temen real life.

author: @letshavefun2270
text:
Haloooo ganteng-gantenganya Noona, 
Happy 6th anniversary yaaaa. 

Gak berasa udah 6 taun jalan bareng kalian. Mungkin Noona gak ngikutin kalian dari awal debut bangeet. Tapi seneng bisa jalan sama kalian dari mulai dapet 1st win, mulai di recognize di dunia musik Korea, disandingin sama grup2 besar lainnya, mulai go internasional. Pencapaian kalian selama 6 tahun debut itu luar biasa bangeeeeet. I'm so proud of you all.. 

Semakin tinggi kalian terbang, ptasti akan makin kenceng "tekanan" yang akan kalian dapet. But please don't worry, carats will always have your back. Jadi terbang yang tinggi, lakuin apa yang mau kalian lakuin. Kita akan support terus, no matter what. 

Yang penting, kalian bahagia, kalian senang ngelakuin semuanya. Karena itu yang Carat mau liat. Kalian bahagia, kalian sehat. 

To a my fellow Carats, please standby them till the end. We need to support each other back. No matter what. 

Note: seneng banget liat komen isinya banyak Carat Indonesia. Luv. 

I'll be back with english comment soon. Kekeke.

author: @fatmanuragustin
text:
Dear seventeen
Makasih udah datang diwaktu yang tepat walau sedikit terlambat. Jujur aku awalnya ga pernah minat sama kpop, cuma ngikutin kdrama. Aku masuk kefandom carat setelah nonton Knowing Brother eps. 252, tau eps itu juga dari akun fanbase nya suju. Dan jujur lagi, aku  ngefans karena kalian ga pernah gagal bikin ketawa (re:lawak:v) sampai akhirnya aku kepoin semua lagu" kalian. Pertama aku tertarik ke jeonghan, aku search di google agak kaget yang muncul jeonghan jaman longhair sempet ngira seventeen ada member cewek (mian jeonghan). Dan bias aku sekarang mingyu wonwoo mungkin bentar lagi oleng karna liat video uji kibas" rambut:(( sejauh ini aku liat gada yg toxic fans, jujur senyaman ini difandom carat. Semoga bisa ketemu lagi di anniversary tahun depan yaa.
Yang udah baca ini makasih
SEVENTEEN SERANGHAE

author: @ambrcm
text: Seeing this makes me teared up a bit, seriously. Can't believe that in yours 6 years journey, I've been there with you for 5 years, it still make me amazed how long yet short the time is. I still remember when I'm just a 14 year old girl, watching all of your amazing content, watching how each member becoming adult until now I've become an adult myself. I still remember all the laughs and tears I've let out for you guys, you guys are literally one of the reason I grow up well and I really want to thank you guys for it, I really appreciate it. There's so much experiences we've been through together for the past years, the good one and the bad one, but I still enjoyed it because we can get through it together. I know there's only a small percentage of you guys seeing this comment of mine, but I just want to say that I love you guys so much and thank you so much for the past years, I hope there'll be more things to wait in the future, because I'll definitely be there until the last say the name. ì„¸ë´‰ì•„ ì‚¬ë‘í•´!

author: @nvnchi5048
text:
I became a carat or a â€œsm17eâ€ back in 2015. I was a freshman in high school then, and I was having a rough time, nearly slipping into depression from just being overwhelmed by schoolwork and my social life. Thankfully these 13 wonderful men came into my life and brought me so much joy and hope. As i got more into the kpop world, i discovered other groups and fell in love with other groups, but iâ€™ve always had a special spot in my heart for seventeen. Back then when I started stanning svt, I didnâ€™t really think much about if they would make it big in the industry or not; I just knew that I really loved their music and their personalities, and thatâ€™s what drew me to them. I wish other people can see them as how I see them. Growing up with svt, Iâ€™ve watched them go from these boys who had to use earphones as in-ear monitors and recycled clothes for performances to these 13 successful yet humble men who are still gaining more popularity each day. I am now almost a junior in college and Iâ€™d just like to say thank you to seventeen for being with me this entire journey, and I promise I will be with them on their journey until the end. I seriously canâ€™t imagine my life without seventeen. My love throughout the years has only grown especially throughout this pandemic.
SEVENTEEN, thank you for everything that you do for us carats (and cubics haha). I know you guys know how influential you are being well known kpop idols, but I seriously cannot describe how much youâ€™ve impacted so many lives and how much of a blessing you all are. From your music, your bright personalities, and just your presence â€” you all are just truly heaven-sent. Thank you for staying with us all these years. Thank you for working so hard even though youâ€™re tired. Thank you for taking the time out of your busy day to just simply send messages on weverse. I wish everyone in the world can see how amazing you all are. I wish you more success in the future, and I know you all will get what you truly deserve in due time. If I could give you the universe, I would.
We love you so much, SEVENTEEN! We promise weâ€™ll be with you until the last say the name. Happy 6th year anniversary ğŸ’–ğŸ’™ğŸ’

text:
Hai Seventeen, Aku salah satu dari jutaan Carat di dunia ini yang jatuh cinta dengan kalian

Tiada hari tanpa rasa terima kasih dan bersyukur telah mengenal kalian. Jujur setelah mengenal kalian dari 6 tahun yang lalu, kalian telah merubah hidupku, kalian membuatku bertahan dari kerasnya dunia ini. Terima kasih Seventeen telah hadir ke dalam hidupku, baru kali ini aku merasakan rasanya cinta dua arah, semua ketulusan yang kalian berikan untukku, semua kerja keras yang kalian lakukan untuk Carat. Aku rasa berucap Terima Kasih saja tidak cukup untuk membalas apa yang sudah kalian berikan. Tapi aku benar-benar berterima kasih atas semuanya (dan aku rasa beberapa Carat pun berfikir demikian).

Seventeen mari kita terus bersama selamanya, bahagia selamanya bersama-sama sampai kalian benar-benar mewujudkan konser diumur 60 tahun kan? Mari kita bertemu pada saat itu

Maaf aku tidak terlalu pandai mengungkapkan perasaanku apalagi merangkai kata kata indah. Tapi dari apa yang aku katakan diatas, aku hanya ingin kalian tahu bahwa aku benar benar bersyukur dan berterima kasih pada kalian (entah sudah berapa kali kata Terima Kasih ini terucap)

I really love you so much Seventeen, We love you so much and let's meet together in the future

Happy 6th Anniversary Seventeen

author: @lena_nguyen17
text:
Dear Seventeen,
I remembered the very first time I stumbled upon One Fine Day season 1 where Dino was ranking the members. I found it funny to see the chaos. Then I started to get into your music after seeing your performance in the KPOP Music Festival for 2016. Your performance was first. My first reaction was, â€œWow how are they so talented?â€ Then I noticed that even when performing, you all had your fun even though on stage. Then Donâ€™t Wanna Cry era came in and I was obsessed the with MV and the song itself, itâ€™s still my favorite song this day. During this time, from December of 2016 to June of 2018, I felt lonely. In middle school a lot of people were bad influences and usually talked badly about me because of my smartness, even though they used me for it. But it didnâ€™t feel all that lonely, because I had Seventeen there. Seventeen felt like a nice comfort in school. In high school, my first two years were horrible. I kept going through an in and out relationship with someone. In 2019-2020, I was thinking of suicide because I couldnâ€™t handle the pain anymore. The person had hurt me so much I lost it. But your music and voices and the funny content in Going Seventeen really helped me cope. Thank you Seventeen for being a place I can run away to. For being a second home. Thank you for helping me realize I am more than just someone to be used. Thank you for giving me confidence to be me again. Happy 6 Years!

author: @biancanooraini744
text:
Dearest seventeen, my precious diamondsğŸ’ğŸ’–

Makasih banyak udah bertahan dan berkembang, melambung semakin tinggi, seiring berjalannya waktu gak berasa udah 6 tahun kita bersama. 

Mungkin aku belum bisa jadi carat yang terbaik, tapi fandom inilah rumah aku. Meskipun beberapa kali aku pergi menjauh tapi tetap pulangnya kesini. Cuma 13 manusia hebat nan kuat inilah yang bilang ke aku "terimakasih telah terlahir di dunia". Cuma dirumah inilah aku merasa seakan aku manusia yang sangat berharga untuk mereka.

Untuk keluargaku, carats. Semoga kita bisa terus bertahan, bersama sama kita bisa terbang lebih tinggi lagi. Tetaplah jadi carat yang terlalu sibuk mencintai seventeen untuk terlibat dalam konflik apapun. Kita fokus untuk saling menyayangi satu sama lain. 

Terimakasih banyak Seventeen dan semua orang yang terlibat dalam kelahirannya 13 berlian ini.

Let's make more beautiful memories in the futureğŸ’–

author: @deboradeby2679
text:
Dear Seventeen 
from one of Carats Indonesia

Aku kenal kalian dari twitter pas tahun 2013 waktu tembok hijau dan kepoin kalian di SEVENTEEN TV haha udh lama bgt kan?  terus aku merasa bahwa aku harus STAN grup ini. Setelah 2 tahun berlalu, 2015 akhirnya kalian debut "ADORE U"  and immediately i'm adore them. Tapi karena kesibukan aku dan fokus ke terhadap yang lain tahun 2017 aku mulai rest dari kpop dan Seventeen. Setelah tidak terlalu addict dgn kpop dan lanjutkan kehidupanku sampai tahun 2020 saat Covid19 menyerang dan kebosanan menghadang, kalian dengan Going Seventeen  dan konten lainnya berhasil membuat ku semangat dan tertawa lepas tdk sperti sebelumnya,  kalian menarik aku KEMBALI kemana aku berada. 
SEVENTEEN THANK YOU FOR EVERY THING , YOU BRINGS A SMILE, HAPPINESS AND COURAGE FOR ME. 

HAPPY 6TH ANNIVERSARY.

author: @ihatereigen
text: Happiest 6th anniversary, angels :) You're truly something out of this world. Thank you for being each others family, thank you for being more family to me than anything else, ever. I hope you don't experience exhausting things you can't do anything about, and that no matter what happens, the thought of leaving each other will always be pushed far, far back and away. And I also hope, that if you do experience things you can't do anything about, you may overcome it. As Seventeen, or not as Seventeen, you deserve to be happy together. I hope that when you look at yourself, you see the person you've always wanted to become when you were a kid. And if not, I hope you see a person that you like right now, someone you're happy to be. No matter how difficult it gets, it's always going to be the thirteen of you. I just know it will.

text:
Time goes by so quickly. You've been making music for the past six years. I'm grateful that I was able to spend my youth with you and I'm thankful that I got to meet you all. From the moment I first became a carat until now, your music and performances have never failed to astonish me. You've spent many sleepless nights striving to become better at what you do. You guys are incredible.You are the most wonderful thing that has ever happened to me. You all helped me a lot, and a simple thank you isn't enough. Even after the last say the name seventeen, I will continue to back you and cheer you on. Thank you for bringing light and joy into my life. You guys are my lifelines.You guys grew up so well. It's been my happiest journey seeing you come so far. I hope we will be able to spend a long time together. We've been holding each other's hands for the past six years! author: @jiedeguzman9591
text:
Dear ì„¸ë¸í‹´,

I honestly couldn't believe I would slip to diamond life.  So here's my story on how I even loved you more. It was November 2020 that time. As I was scrolling through my youtube, I discovered one of the episodes of GOSE and watched it out of curiousity. I find it interesting and fun until I started to watch every episodes, got to know your names, followed your social media accounts and even listened one of your songs. And then in a blink of an eye, I fell in love deeper and deeper. Listening to your songs makes me calm, relaxed, excite, lonely, nostalgic, and happy. All my life, I've never felt so amazed and captivated like that every time I think of you. I am so glad that I entered such a wonderful family-like-fandom and met 13 talented, handsome, humble, charismatic, funny, lovely and amazing boys. Although I'm just a new carat, I will do my best to support and love you.

Thank you for debuting, thank you for making songs and performances that inspired so many people around the world. Thank you so much and Happy 6th Anniversary.
 
Love, CARAT

author: @cintialantiraaragani6285
text:
Hi, ini aku Cintia Lantira. Makasih ya yang udah baca komenan ini, aku seneng banget dan bersyukur juga Allah SWT ngenalin aku SEVENTEEN. Aku sebelumnya ngalamin krisis, aku sempet down karena gak daftar ke SMA impian aku karena terhalang nilai, orang tua aku marah dan kecewa sama aku karena sebelumnya aku sering masuk top 10 seangkatan dan sewaktu nilai UN diumumin aku gak masuk top 10. Aku terpaksa masuk SMK. 

Untungnya setelah sebulan masuk SMK, aku tertarik SEVENTEEN dengan MV Hit yang muncul di beranda YouTube, setelah itu aku penasaran sama mereka. Akhirnya aku memutuskan untuk menjadi penggemar mereka. Banyak banget positif vibes selama aku suka mereka, aku jadi belajar mencintai diri sendiri, belajar tanggung jawab, perlahan pemikiran aku terbuka dan masih banyak lagi kok perubahan yang aku dapat.

Makasih ya SEVENTEEN udah jadi temen di masa remaja aku.

Makasih buat SEVENTEEN jadi penghibur dikala aku sedih dan terpuruk.

Makasih  buat SEVENTEEN bikin aku sembuh perlahan-lahan dari trauma-trauma yang aku alami.

Makasih buat SEVENTEEN jadi penyemangat aku ketika aku down karena ortu aku yang strict.

Makasih buat SEVENTEEN udah bikin aku jadi salah satu alasan untuk percaya diri.

Makasih juga buat CARAT, kalian juga sama halnya seperti SEVENTEEN.
Kalian itu berharga buat aku.

Dear Mingyu, makasih ya udah jadi support system aku. Moodbooster aku, cukup liat wajah kamu aja udah bangkitin semangat aku.

Aku udah suka SEVENTEEN dari Agustus 2019, sekarang Mei 2021.
Harapan aku, aku pengen banget nemenin kalian sampai kalian mencapai tujuan kalian.
Aku pengen tahu, sejauh mana aku masih seneng kalian.
Seandainya aku udah gak lagi ngefans kalian. Aku pengen kenangan kalian akan selalu aku ingat, karena kalian berharga buat aku.


Thanks for ur exictense, i love u so much. 

Dear S.COUPS, Jeonghan, Joshua, Jun, Hoshi, Wonwoo, Woozi, DK, Mingyu, The8, Seungkwan, Vernon, Dino. Kuharap kalian baik baik saja, lakukan yang terbaik bagi kalian, asalkan kalian tau, aku bangga sama kalian. Buat karya yang terbaik ya, kalian harus selalu ingat kalo ada CARAT yang selalu ada disisi kalian.

author: @imcarathohoho6894
text:
Bagai bunga di ladang kering. 
Kalian hadir sebagai setangkai harapan yang dengan ajaibnya bisa ngebuat aku terbius percaya, bahwa kesuksesan itu selalu hadir bersama orang-orang yang selalu bekerja keras. 
Kalian yang buat aku yakin bahwa cinta selalu berjalan bersama tuannya, melewati segala cuaca mendung duka dan terang suka. 
Kalian yang dengan sederhana menunjukkan definisi dari keluarga dan sahabat adalah mereka yang selalu bersama entah di saat kalian jatuh, dan bergerak bangun untuk melanjutkan langkah. 
Kalian udah menjadikan guyonan ku yang awalnya tidak tercapai menjadi sangat receh. 
Kalian, SEVENTEEN, 13 orang bertalenta, 13 orang yang paling bersinar, 13 orang hebat yang bisa membuktikan bahwa menjadi idol bukan sekedar mencapai tonggak prestasi yang dibikin standar orang banyak, tetapi idol adalah siapa yang bisa menyampaikan pesan dan rasa lewat musik yang kalian buat. 
Makasi, udah berhasil membuat ruang kosong hati dan hariku menjadi penuh dengan kesedihan dan kegembiraan. 
Makasi, udah ngasi warna di hatiku yang sudah lama kosong tak berperasa. 

Happy 6th anniversary sebongieee, sehat sehat yaa, semoga tetap jadi setangkai bunga harapan buat carats<3

text: Mau ikutan cerita juga dong hahaha. Waktu itu, gue lagi di kelas akhir dan mulai bingung harus lanjut kemana. Gue ikut tes dua kali dan gagal semua, sedih banget intinya, udah stress banget mau kaya gimana gue kedepannya nanti mau kaya apa, udahnya waktu itu keadaan ekonomi keluarga gue lagi anjlok-anjloknya ditambah ngebayar pendaftaran gue buat lanjut sekolah belum lagi adek gue yang masuk sekolah barengan. Kebiasaan lama gue buat nyakitin diri sendiri hampir aja keulang lagi kalau gue gak iseng buka youtube lihat mv Seventeen seliweran, akhirnya seharian itu gue puas-puasin nangis sambil nontonin video kalian. Energi gue berasa kaya balik lagi, ajaib banget gak sih? Wkwkwk, akhirnya gue nyoba buat gabung jadi carat dan gue ngerasa dapet support sistem yang bisa mendorong gue buat berjuang dikit lagi. Intinya sih, gue gak tau gue sekarang bakal kaya apa dan gimana kalau dulu gak iseng lihat kalian sih hahaha. author: @ãƒãƒ¬ãƒ³ã‚ºã‚¨ãƒ©ãƒ¡ã‚¢ãƒªãƒ¼ã‚°ãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¹
text:
I've gotten to know Seventeen in 2016. My long time friend have already recommended SVT to me months prior but i didn't really checked them out bc i was already a long time fan of another group. 
One time I was in a bad headspace and was really down and confused about a lot of things (fandom related included). I wanted to  take all the negativity off and told myself I need a change. Then I remember my friend recommending Seventeen. So i listened to their 1st album 17carat and have enjoyed the songs. I remember I was on my commute home then. I have already enjoyed the first few songs from that album, then the last song "20" played... and I was just really overwhelmed  with feelings. I can't believe how a song can easily uplift my mood like that and it was my first time listening to it too. Since then, i started searching about them and watching their stuff. It is easier to catch up then bc they only had like one full album and 2 singles but it never mattered to me even if i just kept repeating the same 20+ songs. I love listening to them and I love the feeling of joy and comfort they are giving me thru their songs. Eventually they released more songs and contents and I ended up being a full blown Carat. I started with 2nd gen official membership, I still am a Carat to this day. And seeing them accomplish more things thru their passion and hardwork, it makes me so so proud of them. I hope they can achieve even bigger dreams in the future. And I promise to be a Carat helping in their journey then. ğŸ’“ happy anniversary my loves.

author: @ShavinaPutriFronatics
text: to my dearest, my home, my seventeen, my never-ending crush, my comfortable place, my everything. your existence is nothing less than a miracle itself, and i am most grateful for it. it strenghten me, even when my life is full of atrociousness in it. i've never felt this in love towards someone else, indeed this kind of feeling was scarcely general for me to feel towards someone. and once again i'm so thankful that this kind of feelings of course towards you guys, kept me alive. no one in the world would know how to describe in words, how thankful i am to know your presence. we may not in the same place, but i bet our hearts are. i hope this pandemic will end soon, and hoping to get the opportunities to meet you in the same place eventually. i'm still waiting, and i'm not tired, not ever. please do be healthy and take good care and give yourselves lots of love and encouragement because you guys deserve it so much. thank you for everything, i couldn't write enough of how much i am grateful, but let's walk on this flowery paths together, intertwine our fingers and never let go. last but not least, thank you for making me the happiest woman alive. most ardently, i love youğŸ’–

author: @princessmaellevares8477
text: It was the summer of 2016 when I met these beautiful and amazingly multitalented people. It was not intended, no one introduced them to me. I just somehow found their video in my cousin's gallery, it was like we were soulmates. It was meant to happen. At first I thought, "Oof, Kpop? Meh," I admit, I was really not into Kpop before. I just did not like them, and I did not even know why. But when I clicked their videos and listened to their songs "Pretty U" and "Adore U", I immediately liked them. The first member that attracted my attention was Jun. Then, I became even more curious about them. I watched mor of their videos. Even paused in the middle of it just to count the members, making sure if there were really seventeen memb or not HAHAHAHAHA. I started to download their videos and songs, and listen to them 24/7. Even tried singing with them, practicing my Korean skills HAHAHAHAHA. And before I could knew it, I was already into the Diamond Life. I also want to give gratitude to my friend who kept me updated, hyped, and crazy over Seventeen. She really was a big factor in my fangirling life. SEVENTEEN is my first love in Kpop, while CARAT is my first fandom. Both will forever and will always be my home, until my last.

text:
Seeing my co-carat shared their story on how they met Seventeen, I had the urge to share mine, too. Hehe
So, it all started when Seventeen's Left and Right Mafia Dance on Dingo's channel played next. I was actually watching NCT Dream's We Go Up Mafia Dance. Without hesitation, I started the video and I remembered laughing all the time. They were hilarious and funny. Apart from it, I can see the sincerity of their friendship and the strong bond they have from the video. I may not know them very well at that point, but, there's this connection that I felt, a tingling feeling in my heart. I mean, I mean it. From then on up until today, their 6th year in the industry, I still shine as their diamond.^^ 

Dear Seventeen,
You have been one of my comfort. Your songs are very sincere that though I play it everytime, I'm still having goosebumps. God bless y'all!

author: @elaiza4932
text:
Thank you so much for this wonderful music! Thank you Seventeen. ğŸ’—

Happy 6th Anniversary to us! First of all, I wanted to say thank you for all the love and support you are constantly giving to carats. May the bright paint colors your life sebongie because you'll deserve all that and more. I wish you'll good health, happiness, wealth, and success. Also, I truly believe that you'll are very talented in every aspect that you all have shown us so far, and I wish you the best at everything you do! I also hope your days are always filled with love! please don't forget to take care of yourself and stay safe! hopefully one day SEVENTEEN will be able to come again to the Philippines. I love you, and again, take care. I am proud that seventeen remained firm to their brand. Despite the risk they face every time they release new music, they chose to focus on expressing their thoughts & feelings and dedicate the message to their fans, carats. I will always love you Sebongie, until forever. Thank you for inspiring us to do our best, thank you for giving us so much happiness. You make my day.

author: @Aya-jx5fk
text: My heart is full of your love. It is totally enlarged that I feel like I am floating in cloud nine. When I discovered you guys, I thought that you guys might be interesting boy group and I stand corrected. Entering the carat life is one of the best things that I have ever done. Not one group that I had stan have ever made me feel this happy, content, and even felt treasured by you guys. The love that you showered us carats may be in general but it never once felt like that. Every 'I love you', 'take care', 'we miss you', 'see you', and 'be safe' never felt so fake. Every fiber of my being tremble each time you guys say those words to us. I may not be one of your best supporters out there, but I truly appreciate and love what you guys are doing. Your music gave me the strength every time I am down, gave me joy in my lonely days, and gave me the love everyday. Happy Anniversary SVT! Until the last 'Say the name' even after that I will be supporting you guys! :))))))

Happy 6th birthday seventeenâ™¡
Ga nyangka udah 6 tahun sejak aku ketemu kalian pertamakali di tahun 2015. Dalam 6 thn ini aku menyaksikan kalian tumbuh. Dari kelahiran carat, pengumuman warna fandom, 1st win pertama kalian, 1st rookie award, sampe daesang pertama kalian. Seventeen itu kayak bagian dr masa remajaku wkwk. Kalian udah spt teman  dan keluargaku. Tiap lihat mv lama kalian tuh rasanya 'gila, sekarang udah gede mereka' wkwkwkwk

Tapi ada 1 hal yg bener2 ga berubah dari kalian. Passion dan semangat kalian diatas panggung kalian g pernah luntur dan pasti PASTI tiap cb baru ada aja yg bikin kaget.

Aku bener2 bersyukur udah menjadi carat, semoga kedepannya (10thn, 20thn, 30thn? Wkwk)  kita bisa terus melangkah bersama ya. Kalau kalian lelah, boleh kok istiharat.

author: @horangisvault4121
text:
Dear SEVENTEEN,

Stanning you guys was the BEST decision I've made ever. I never imagined life could be even more beautiful and lovely. Thank you for giving me the love and comfort the world seems to rob off of me. I wonder how I could ever live without you. You've become my necessity, and the meaning of life itself. I will not promise, because promises are meant to be broken, but I will always, always be there for you, like how you guys would for us, too. Afterall, we're your SEVENTEEN carats! For this 6th Anniversary, I just wish you all evergreen happiness, and good health. I wish you all the best. If I could give you everything, I would, no joke.

text:
Seeing so many carats write their story/thoughts makes me wanna do the same. If I'm being honest, I really don't know what the reason I can become a Carat, like suddenly I slip into diamond life without hesitation. I came to you when you were 4 years old, in 2019. In 2019, so many things happened to me, from the happiest thing to the worst thing (me and my best friends had the fighting at that time, maybe 3 months of fighting? Really). I have anxiety, but I listen to your songs that healed me, made me a better person, friend, and sister. I've been in a fandom before Carat, but in this fandom, it's so comfortable, meet so many carats, talk with them, carats, thank you for always being who you are, I love you, thank you for always supporting our boys, let's always support them until the last say the name. 
And to our boys, sebong, thank you for everything, keep doing what you like, because your happiness is ours too. We love you so much, thank you for coming to Carat's life â™¡â™¡

HAPPY 6TH ANNIVERSARY to this 13 wonderful guys, I became carat in this past few months and they already become a comfort place for me. I was at my lowest when I came across their music, just by hearing their voices suddenly I felt fine as if I  never felt bad all these times, this feeling was so new for me,cause after so long I felt it, for once I was okay for real.  I've found comfort in each smile of them,they are really precious for me, since they gave me back that strength that I thought to have already lost. I was so unmotivated before I found them, but they made me realize, I can do it, it take too long maybe to raise again but after so many tries I success
this 13 guys and carat really mean so much for me, thank you! Your guys presence in enough for me. And always remember, you can do it!
(sorry for my bad English)

author: @nadyaray.s799
text:
One of my friend once said that Seventeen won't last long because they have a lot of members. She said it in 2017, but... Look... It's 2021 now and she's wrong.  Seventeen has never lost a single member and has remained 13 for 6 years since they debuted.

For my Lovely Seventeen,
Thank you, Seventeen, for becoming Seventeen. Thank you, Seventeen, for standing and staying there for us. Thank you, Seventeen, for becoming my strength whenever I want to give up. I said thank you. I love you all.  You are my home, my beloved home.

And, for my Beloved CARAT,
Thank you for all of your support. Thank you for being on my side. Thank you for staying here for our Seventeen. Thank you, I said Thank You. I love you all, CARAT, my lovely and beloved home.


For Seventeen and CARAT from all over the world,
Let's stay together untill the last *Say The Name* âœ¨


Terima kasih, Seventeen
Terima kasih, CARAT
Aku mencintai kalian semua â¤ï¸

text: I'm a new carat and I'm really grateful for knowing SVT. These past few months have been really hard for me. I slowly can't remember the things that used to make me feel happy. I'm trying to get better, but sometimes it's just so exhausting to try and fail over and over again. But ever since I knew all of you, I've been feeling much better. Y'all always make me laugh and cry in joy. The effort y'all and the staffs put into everything y'all do is seriously awesome. Even "awesome" is not enough to describe it. Your hard work makes me realize that there's still a hope inside me. A hope to survive, to enjoy living this life, to watch y'all grow and grow together with y'all. Please stay safe, healthy, and hydrated. May your day be filled with happiness and joy. We love y'all <3

author: @juliacarat
text:
Happy 6th anniversary dear seventeen !
I am really sorry that I wasn't here since day one but I promise I will be here until the very end :)
You are probably not going to ever read this and I know that but I want you guys to know that you are my one and only inspiration, I learnt a lot of things from you and I must say I love and appreciate my family much more than before because of you.
Hug, smile flower, us again and so many of your songs can always make me feel better even when I am facing very hard times.
In fact seventeen can make me cry, laugh, smile and even scream with even as little as a picture or a short video.
I even started learning Korean just because you got me to like this language :)
From the bottom of my heart I want you to know that I love you and I will support you forever and always, thank you so much for those 6 beautiful years, let's continue this journey together ^~^

author: @aihara3463
text:
It's only my thought but As much as I love Seventeen and I hope they become so much bigger than now, still (in deep my heart more than that) I just wish they can shine this beautifully enough for a long long time.  And I just wish we can love them this naturally enough as we are like now. Where we can enjoy their music happily without too much burden and greedy for such acknowledgment, achievement, etc. 

Don't take me wrong, I said it first, ofcourse I want they become bigger too, but let it be in natural ways. Since I have no doubt about Seventeen's Qualities and Hardwork, so I believe they only will be bigger and bigger in future...

author: @aparajitapal7834
text: Seventeen and carats love for each other will never be enough. The pandemic separated us physically but I truly believe that carats will always have seventeen because of their songs and other contents. Seventeen is talented, not just in terms of singing, dancing and rapping but also in their ability to feel like a warm blanket on a cold winter night. Seventeen always surprise us. They motivate us to do better, to make our own decisions and follow our dreams and to take a break when there is too much. I myself didn't stan them from the beginning but that does not matter. I found them and I promise that I won't leave till the last say the name. Seventeen, you make my dawn and my day. You protect us and we protect you. I am proud of Seventeen and proud to be a carat. Our futures are truly indefinite but whatever is instore for us, you make the journey beautiful. And no matter what happens, we will meet again.

text:
Untuk member SEVENTEEN, terimakasih udah ada dan hadir sebagai SEVENTEEN. 
Menjadi Carat adalah salah satu keputusan yg sama sekalipun ga akan aku sesali dalam hidup. Karena seberuntung itu, rasanya bukan hanya punya kalian sebagai idol ku tapi punya kalian sebagai temen bahkan sahabat yang semangatin dan ngerti perasaan aku lewat lagu kalian, bikin aku ketawa lewat tingkah kalian, dan bikin aku terharu juga lewat surat kalian. 
Kalian berhasil ngealihin pikiran aku dengan baik, pikiran yg seringkali buat aku down bahkan sakit terus terus an. Tapi karena SEVENTEEN perlahan aku semangat lagi, punya tujuan hidup lagi dan mulai belajar mencintai diri sendiri apapun keadaannya. 

Intinya I love u guys, i loveee u so much, ayo bahagia selamanya! 
Selamat anniversary yg ke 6 Semoga bisa ngerayaain lagi sampe ke 7,8,9 atau bahkan 10 tahun lagi. 

Tapi satu hal yg pasti aku akan terus suport kalian^^
Maunya pake bahasa inggris barangkali kalian scroll dan baca tapi skill aku masih pasif hehe

author: @mynameis_kayepop6097
text:
I got teary eyed watching this. It's like everything they went through just flash before my eyes from their trainee days to the current them. I've been a fan of theirs since they're debut era and I'm really proud to call myself a Carat, I'm not just a fan but a family. The boys have become my family and my source of happiness in a world full of negativity. I'm thankful to have seen them in personal (through concerts) and experienced how true to themselves these boys are. They really make you feel like you're a part of their group, their friendship. No matter when you became a fan, you'll never fail to feel attached to them and wonder what their next step will be. You wish to see more of their growth and how they managed to stay humble and true amidst all diversities and their popularity.

I'm probably rambling now but I'm really just thankful to SEVENTEEN and wish them the best every step of the way. I only pray their friendship will last long.
